\id REV  
\h KURÕ FESIYA OD 
\toc1 Kurõ Fesiya Od 
\toc2 Kurõ Fesiya Od 
\toc3 Kurõ Fesiya Od 
\mt1 Kurõ Fesiya Od  
\c 1  
\s1 Od Uyu Irouya  
\p
\v 1 Jesus Kristus nẽ kurõ fesiya od, are ereb kaisã bagai wõ youf anĩ, Negurem yogon ferfer ifelnẽdiyouf nigin Jesus ifenen. Jesus ĩ, yogon ferfer Jon od anĩ keleĩ youf nigin, yogon engel Jon bun sur fen.  
\v 2 Jonem ereb ereb ganan ĩ ilen anĩ kurõ falaisif, are Negur nẽ od ado, Jesus Kristus nẽ od.  
\v 3 Taka ĩ profet od enei iwesef are ĩ el fiyek, agef fen, idi anĩ karĩ de fen, ereb anĩ bun itoton anĩ waud bun dinof anidi el fedif, ere nigin, sain mogo dodolef.   
\s1 Jon Sios Sewen Bun Yogon Aanya Sur Fen  
\p
\v 4 Aya Jon,  
\p Asia provins bun sios sewen bun pas enei atotof.  
\p Negur ĩ gama ibodok, kulu ibodon, dumen isiyouf bunem, uur sewen yogon king nẽ sia wagen difaref bunem ado,  
\v 5 Jesus Kristus ĩ Negur nẽ od el fe dõf wogõ yedig, ĩ tamo gare den bun tamal uyulil kel turĩ fiyen, tenebur king ganan neid mudur ĩ bunem, wau ifenẽya ado wau inosiya ã bun isif.  
\p Jesus ĩ ada nigin wau laaf fen, yogon naud bunem, ada neda mosor bun tamal yalelnadan.  
\v 6 Agef fen, ĩ ada yogon Tama Negur aruna yaleya nigin, in tano ado in pris inodan. Ĩ bun fula fiya medeĩya ado megeir gai gai ibodkalauf! Momoi.   
\q1
\v 7 Log, ĩ lalo bunem isif.  
\q2 Age fe di, meleid ganan ĩ dilouf,  
\q1 idi ĩ gilĩ difen anidig dilouf.  
\q2 Age fe di, tamo kayau tenebur ein ganan ĩ nigin waud gudũ fouf.  
\q2 Are agef bagai wõ youf! Momoi.   
\p
\v 8 Odug Negur irok, “Aya uyulil ado idikeleya, aya gama abodok, kulu abodon, dumen asiyouf, aya saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri afeid uyu aroudig anĩ.”   
\s1 Taka Ĩ Tamo Naal Gen  
\p
\v 9 Aya Jon, ãgenei tureĩ, aya, Jesus bun darau, Negur nẽ tano ado, feseya sã ifareya, ã geid taledig, aya Negur nẽ od ado Jesus nẽ od wogõ aun nigin, Patmos nuyo bun abodon.  
\v 10 Odug nẽ naa bun, aya Awa Uur namen abod ken, aya dumeun ait odug taur gen wõ ye mog, karĩ aun.  
\v 11 Ait iron, “Ereb õ ulef anĩ, buk kori fiya bun utot fen, sios sewen bun sur wediyouf, oun Efesus, Smerna, Pergamum, Taiataira, Sardis, Filadelfia ado, Laodisia.”   
\p
\v 12 Aya ait wogõ fiyan anĩ ileya nigin falei aun. Aya falei aul fen, lam nẽ gol tutur sewen ailedin.  
\v 13 Lam tutur anĩ atun, aib taka “tamo naal gen”\f + \fr 1:13  \ft Daniel 7:13\f* kolos meluk ifonũ di, yen isilen ado, let gol akor gu fen anĩ ifaren.  
\v 14 In mudur ado fatiya, sipsip siwi lalau, saa lalo lalau gen, yogon mala are yã mala fitotoleya gen.  
\v 15 Yogon ye are bras yã malan ifalegeya medeĩya gen, in ait are naan uhuhuya gen.  
\v 16 Yogon ima biyalẽ barisa sewen iroun, agef fen, in awa bun tamal, dimig bala waila si sitakã wõ yen. Yogon nawa are gaa ririya gen medeĩ yen.   
\p
\v 17 Aya ĩ ail fen, aya ĩ ye gariyan kubũ au, laa gen ainen. Age afe di, ĩ ima biyalẽ aya teteun ino fen, iron, “Õ to kumĩ wo. Aya gariya, aya idikeleya.  
\v 18 Aya mata ibodõya nẽ, aya laa fiyan, anĩ ere, uleyaf, aya gai gai mata abodkalauf! Aya laa nẽ ado Hades nẽ ki aroudif.   
\p
\v 19 “Anĩ nigin, ereb õ ulen, ereb gama ibodok, ereb dumen wõ youf anĩ utot.  
\v 20 Barisa sewen aya imau biyalẽ ulen ado, lam nẽ gol tutur sewen ulen anĩ nẽ waa nẽ gariya, are eig fiya: Barisa sewen are sios sewen neid engel, lam nẽ tutur sewen are sios sewen.   
\c 2  
\s1 Efesus Sios Bun Od Ilef  
\p
\v 1 “Efesus sios nẽ engel bun utot:  
\pi1 Od enei are, ĩ barisa sewen ima biyalẽ irou mog, sewen gol lam tutur difaren atun iyok ilen nẽ od:  
\v 2 Ereb õ ago wof, are aya keleĩ, ogon kabĩ totol yaleya ado ogon feseya sã ifareya anĩ. Aya keleĩ, õ tamo sesen to loloum weid fen, idi dogo anĩ aposel dedig, anĩ ere, aposel sã anidi es wiyeĩd fen, idi neid idegẽya anĩ ulen.  
\v 3 Õ totol ufar fen, neu yanau nigin morõ faali won, anĩ ere, õ to fõ yon.   
\pi1
\v 4 Anĩ ere, aya õ nigin od enei ado: Õ uruwa aya nigin waũ laa fen anĩ utoron.  
\v 5 Anĩ nigin, õ nainenem kubũ won anĩ kisi wo! Falei wo fen, ereb uruwa agon anĩ agouf. Õ to falei wouf are, aya õ gein asi fen, ogon lam tutur ado yogon modoũ bun tamal alelauf.  
\v 6 Anĩ ere, tobonunã biya enei õ ado: Õ Nikolas dõ difiyek neid tobonuneid to oroyõdig, are ayag to oroudig.   
\pi1
\v 7 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ Awa Uur sios irokenẽdif anĩ karĩ youf. Aib ĩ kusĩ anĩ wal fouf, aya ĩ mata ifenẽya nẽ aa Negur nẽ paradis bun ibodok anĩ bun tamal, yõya nigin yo afiyẽf.   
\s1 Smerna Sios Bun Od Ilef  
\p
\v 8 “Smerna sios nẽ engel bun utot:  
\pi1 Od enei are, ĩ gariya ado idikeleya, ĩ laaf fen, baban mata fã yen nẽ od.  
\v 9 Ogon darau ado ogon maleg nigin aya keleĩ, anĩ ere, õ safina musei ado. Aya idi dogo nigin Juda tamo dedig, anĩ ere, idi Juda tamo sã, Satan nẽ guru fiya anidi neid bou yũya od nigin keleĩ.  
\v 10 Ereb mogo õ darau ifonõf nigin to kumĩ wo. Aya õ arokonok, Satan ĩ mogo ã tunĩ kisi yeĩya nigin kalabus bun ineneĩf. Age fe di, ã naa ten darau walogouf. Õ laa bun dinenõfeg, ogon momoiya urou kafĩ walauf, ago di, aya õ mata nẽ teter kurũ ayõf.   
\pi1
\v 11 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ Awa Uur sios irokenẽdif anĩ karĩ youf. Aib ĩ kusĩ anĩ wal fouf, namba tu nẽ laa ĩ to daũ fiyẽf.   
\s1 Pergamum Sios Bun Od Ilef  
\p
\v 12 “Pergamum sios nẽ engel bun utot:  
\pi1 Od enei are, ĩ dimig bala waila si sitakã ado nẽ od.  
\v 13 Õ ubodok nẽ an aya keleĩ, an Satan nẽ sia ibodok. Anĩ ere, õ neu yanau urou kafĩ welef. Antipas, neu dõ fiya biya, aya nigin od wogõ yedig, ĩ Satan ibodok nẽ ãgenei taun an dukesin sain anĩ buneg, õ aya nigin ogon momoiya to folõ welen.   
\pi1
\v 14 Anĩ ere, aya õ nigin od tunĩ ado: Õ tamo tunĩ an Balam nẽ keleĩ dirouf anidi ado, Balam ĩ Balak ifelnẽ di, Balak ĩ Israel tamo kayau yeid tũ fiya nẽ meein ino fen, idegnẽdi di, Israel idi saaf idegẽya waitou bun sesewi difen anĩ dokon, noli tobonunã dinon.  
\v 15 Age fiya gen, õ aneg tunĩ Nikolas nẽ ifelnẽya dirouf anidi ado.  
\v 16 Anĩ nigin, waũ falei wo! Sãf are, aya kaisã bagai õ gein asi fen, neu sigorou nẽ dimig ado idi geid kusĩ auf.   
\pi1
\v 17 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ Awa Uur sios irokenẽdif anĩ karĩ youf. Aib ĩ kusĩ anĩ wal fouf, aya ĩ mana iminẽyan ibodok tunĩ afenẽf. Aya ĩ meein lalau takag, yana mata teten itoton anĩ afenẽf. Aib ĩ anĩ yalef dogol yana anĩ keleĩ youf.   
\s1 Taiataira Sios Bun Od Ilef  
\p
\v 18 “Taiataira sios nẽ engel bun utot:  
\pi1 Od enei are Negur Naal nẽ od, yogon mala are yã mala fitotoleya gen, yogon ye are bras yã malan ifalegeya medeĩya gen.  
\v 19 Aya keleĩ, õ ereb agof, ogon waũ laa fiya ado momoiya, ogon aruna yaleya ado feseya sã ifareya. Aya keleĩ, õ uruwa bun ago won anĩ wal fiya gama õ agodig.   
\pi1
\v 20 Anĩ ere, aya õ nigin od enei ado: Õ kayau Jesebel, ĩ yogo nigin profet kayau yef anĩ, loloum wedig. Ĩ yogon ifelnẽya bunem neu ferfer idegnẽdi di, idi noli tobonunã bun dile fen, saaf idegẽya waitou sesewi difen anĩ dõdig.  
\v 21 Aya ĩ yogon mosor nigin wau falei youf nigin sain afenen, anĩ ere, ĩ to orof.  
\v 22 Anĩ nigin, aya ĩ darau nẽ fatar bun ara ken, idi ĩ geid seseirã dinodig anidi, kayau anĩ nẽ naab nigin waud to falei youf are, aya idi darau fatuk bagai afenẽdiyouf.  
\v 23 Aya ĩ gere tar adenkesiyouf. Age afe di, sios ganan, aya waud ado kisi es afedig anĩ keleĩ youf. Age afe fen, aya ã mugu mugu ereb ereb ã ago gef kilei, mala solo afeneĩf.  
\v 24 Anĩ ere, aya ã tunĩ ganan Taiataira ufaregef anĩ arokeneik, ã kayau anĩ nẽ ifelnẽya to uroug fen, Satan nẽ waa namen bagai dedig anĩ to kelein anĩ arokeneik (aya ã bun ereb morõ taka to afeneĩf).  
\v 25 Ereb ã urougef anĩ dogol urougef uleg mog, asiyouf.   
\pi1
\v 26 Aib ĩ kusĩ anĩ wal fe fen, neu oroya dõf ile, idikeleya bun ouf, aya ĩ teneub lo fediya nigin megeir afenẽf.   
\q1
\v 27 ‘Ĩ ain manig nem ulum irokenẽdiyouf,  
\q2 ĩ mis gen daũ fedi di, urud falaisiyouf,’\f + \fr 2:27  \ft Sam 2:9\f*  
\mi are aya neu Dei bunem megeir alen gen.  
\v 28 Aya ĩ bonimei nẽ barisa kilokilog afenẽf.  
\v 29 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ Awa Uur sios irokenẽdif anĩ karĩ youf.   
\c 3  
\s1 Sardis Sios Bun Od Ilef  
\p
\v 1 “Sardis sios nẽ engel bun utot:  
\pi1 Od enei are, ĩ Negur nẽ uur sewen ado barisa sewen irouf anĩ nẽ od. Õ ereb agof, are aya keleĩ. Õ mata ubodok dedig, anĩ ere, õ laa yon.  
\v 2 Fã wale! Ereb mogo laa fou fenẽ anĩ megeir wenẽ, ere nigin, aya õ ereb agof are neu Negur nẽ mala bun tutuk bagai sã ailef.  
\v 3 Anĩ nigin, ereb õ walen, ereb õ karĩ won anĩ karĩ walauf. Anĩ dõ wo fen, waũ falei wo. Õ to fã walouf are, aya bẽ tamo gen asiyouf. Aya sain nanĩ be, õ gein asiyouf anĩ, õ to keleĩ youf.   
\pi1
\v 4 Anĩ ere, õ, Sardis an tamo kayau tunĩ, idi neid kolos amuyẽ fiya sã difaref anidi ado. Idi kolos lalau difoun ken, aya geid mayõf, ere nigin, idi kisi feleya bagai.  
\v 5 Aib ĩ kusĩ anĩ wal fouf, ĩ idi gen kolos lalau ifonũf. Aya yogon yana, mata ibodõya nẽ buk bun tamal to alelauf, age afe fen, yogon yana neu Dei ado yogon engel meleid bun kurõ afesiyouf.  
\v 6 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ Awa Uur sios irokenẽdif anĩ karĩ youf.   
\s1 Filadelfia Sios Bun Od Ilef  
\p
\v 7 “Filadelfia sios nẽ engel bun utot:  
\pi1 Od enei are, ĩ fateul bagai ado momoi nẽ od, ĩ Dawid nẽ ki irouf. Ereb ĩ kã fef, taka nem to inolalauf, agef fen, ereb ĩ inolelef, taka nem to kã falauf.  
\v 8 Õ ereb agof, are aya keleĩ. Ulef, aya, sukar kã feleya taka nem inoleleya kisi felya sã anĩ, õ wagen anon. Aya keleĩ, õ megeir naal bagai ado, anĩ ere, õ neu od dõ wo fen, neu yanau to wa won.  
\v 9 Ulef, idi Satan nẽ guru fiya namen temeleid, idi dogo nigin Juda tamo dedig, anĩ ere, idi Juda tamo sã, idegẽya tamo anĩ, ayam age afe di, idi disi, õ yẽ gariyan kubũ de fen, aya õ nigin wau laa fedig anĩ idi keleĩ youf.  
\v 10 Õ feseya sã ufarauf nigin neu od urou kafĩ welen anĩ nigin, ayag idi tenebur dibodok kisi fediya nigin teneub ganan bun darau isiyouf sain bun, aya õ ahaha ayõf.   
\pi1
\v 11 Aya kaisã bagai asiyouf. Õ ereb urouf anĩ kafĩ walauf, ago di, taka nem ogon kurũ fiya nẽ teter anĩ to yalouf.  
\v 12 Aib ĩ kusĩ anĩ wal fouf, aya, neu Negur nẽ tempel bun, ĩ monog tor atennẽf. Ĩ anĩ baban to bagai itorõf. Aya ĩ bun, neu Negur nẽ yana ado, neu Negur nẽ taun yana, Jerusalem mata, are saa ilun tamal neu Negur bunem isiyouf anĩ atotauf. Age afe fen, aya neu yanau matag ĩ bun atotauf.  
\v 13 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ Awa Uur sios irokenẽdif anĩ karĩ youf.   
\s1 Laodisia Sios Bun Od Ilef  
\p
\v 14 “Laodisia sios nẽ engel bun utot:  
\pi1 Od enei are Momoi Barikã nẽ od, ĩ dõ fiya biya ado, momoi bagai Negur nẽ od wogõ yedig, ĩ ereb ereb Negur inodin ganan nẽ gariya.  
\v 15 Õ ereb agof anĩ aya keleĩ, are õ medir sã, uruwag sã. Aya õ medir be, uruwa anĩ taka ubodok nigin orouf.  
\v 16 Anĩ nigin, õ laigog, medir sã, uruwag sã nigin, aya õ mogo awau bun tamal atigil arãyõf.  
\v 17 Õ urõdig, ‘Aya safina ganan kisi feleya, aya safina musei alen nigin, aya ereb taka to lau afedig,’ wodig. Anĩ ere, õ keleĩ sã, õ gai sane bagai, malalon ado, maleg, malã ifofakeleya ado, gemũ ubodok.  
\v 18 Aya õ arokonok, õ aya bun gol bagai, gol yã bun difalegen anĩ, õ safina ganan kisi feleya bagai wõ wouf nigin, na walouf, õ kolos lalaug ufonũ di, ogon gemũ mama dede wouf nigin na walouf, õ mala marasin malã bun uno fen, kelẽ walauf nigin na walouf.   
\pi1
\v 19 Aya idi nigin wau laa fedig anidi, aya ou afeid fen, tai afedidig. Anĩ nigin, kabĩ totol wale fen, mosor utor ken, waũ falei wouf.  
\v 20 Lo weleg, aya bobogẽ afar fen, godu afef. Taka ĩ aitou karĩ ye fen, sukar kã fouf are, aya ĩ namen asi fen, ĩ ado saaf mãf, age afe di, ĩ aya ado saaf mãf. \fig Jesus bobogẽ ifar fen, sukar godu fef.|src="cn02107B.tif" size="span" ref="3:20" \fig*   
\pi1
\v 21 Aib ĩ kusĩ anĩ wal fouf, aya kusĩ wal afe fen, neu Dei nẽ king nẽ sia bun, neu Dei ado mabodok gen, ĩg neu king nẽ sia bun, aya ado mabodõf nigin yo afiyẽf.  
\v 22 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ Awa Uur sios irokenẽdif anĩ karĩ youf.”   
\c 4  
\s1 King nẽ Sia Saa Ilun Ibodok  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya kelẽ aulen, aya wageun an saa ilun nẽ sukar kã feleya ifar mog, ailen. Age afe fen, ait aya uyulil taur gen wogõ fiya di, karĩ aun are iron, “Ein use, ago di, ereb enei bure fele di, wõ youf anĩ, afelnõf.”  
\v 2 Kaisã bagai aya Awa Uur namen abodon, age afe fen, wageun an saa ilun king nẽ sia bun, aib taka ibodon anĩ ailen.  
\v 3 Agef fen, taka an ibodon are, lo fiya bun meein medeĩya jaspa ado meein giriya medeĩya konilian gen wõ yen. Walol taka, meein aarau mata age fiya medeĩya emeral gen sof fen, king nẽ sia anĩ kalilĩ fen.  
\v 4 King nẽ sia anĩ sirin, tuwenti-fo king nẽ sia anim salili de fen, tuwenti-fo mudur adodo anĩ bun dibodon. Idi kolos lalau difoun ken, dogo neid mudureid bun king nẽ gol teter ado dibodon.  
\v 5 King nẽ sia bun kolimei filiya firagagaũ fe sof fen, gurũya odug wõ ye di, kolimei gudũ yen. King nẽ sia wagen lam sewen futu redin, are Negur nẽ awa uur sewen anĩ.  
\v 6 Takag, king nẽ sia wagen, ereb taka maaĩ gen galas nem dinon anĩ, galas medeĩya bagai age fiya ibodon.  
\p Anĩ atun king nẽ sia salili fiya bun, ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo difaren. Idi meleid barikã, wagedin ado dumedineg.  
\v 7 Ereb mata ibodõya uyu ifaren are laion gen, anĩ dõ fiya are bulmakau gen, anĩ dõ fiya are nawa, tamo nawa gen, anĩ dõ fiya are webi fatutu yef gen.  
\v 8 Ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo idi mugu mugu wayeid sigis ado fen, bouweid ganan bun meleid barikã, wayeid farumẽg meleid ado. Bõ ado gaa ado, idi eig yeya to folõ difeledig:   
\qc “Fateul, fateul, fateul  
\qc are Odug Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri feid uyu iroudig anĩ,  
\qc ĩ kulu ibodon, ĩ gama ibodok, ĩ dumen isiyouf.”  
\m
\v 9 Ereb sain ereb mata ibodõya idi, taka ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibod ken, mata faimud ibodkeleya anĩ bun, fula fiya medeĩya, yana odug ado, de fiyẽya difenẽdig bun,  
\v 10 mudur adodo tuwenti-fo, ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibod mog, ĩ wagen kuku de fen, ĩ mata faimud ibodkeleya anĩ seli dalesedig. Idi king nẽ sia wagen dogo neid teter gõ difel fen, dirõdig:   
\q1
\v 11 “Nemã Odug Negur,  
\q1 õ fula fiya medeĩya, yana odug ado, megeir yaleya kisi feleya bagai,  
\q1 ere nigin, õ ereb ereb ganan ago di, wowã den,  
\q2 ago fen, ogon oroya bunem idi unodi di,  
\q2 age de difaref.”   
\c 5  
\s1 Buk Kori Fiya Ado Sipsip Naal  
\p
\v 1 Age de di, aya ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibodon anĩ ima biyalẽ, buk kori fiya si sitakã itotoya ado uris sewen nem ĩtã de fen, sile fiyan anĩ ailen. \fig Buk kori fiya si sitakã itotoya ado uris sewen nem ĩtã de fen, sile fiyan anĩ.|src="Boyd-scroll-bb.tif" size="span" ref="5:1" \fig*  
\v 2 Age afe fen, aya engel megeir ado taka ailen, ĩ ait odugem iweig iron, “Aim uris eneidi narĩ feid fen, buk kori fiya enei fara feleya kisi feleya?”  
\v 3 Anĩ ere, saa ilun be, tenebur be, teneub farumen tamal, taka nem buk kori fiya anĩ fara feleya be, namen fele fiya kisi feleya sã.  
\v 4 Aya fatuk bagai inã alen, ere nigin, taka nem buk kori fiya anĩ fara feleya be, namen fele fiya kisi feleya to wõ yen.  
\v 5 Age afe di, mudur adodo takam aya irokanan, “To inã wale! Ulef, Juda nẽ ibor bun tamal Laion, Dawid nẽ Warei mogo kusĩ wal fen. Inim, sã buk kori fiya anĩ yogon ĩtãfiya uris sewen ado fara falauf.”   
\p
\v 6 Age ye di, aya Sipsip Naal dukesin anĩ gen, king nẽ sia ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo salili difiyen ado, mudur adodo atun ifar mog, ailen. Ĩ karat sewen ado mala sewen ado, mala sewen are Negur nẽ awa uur sewen teneub ganan bun susur fedin anidi.  
\v 7 Sipsip Naal ĩ isi fen, ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibodon anĩ nẽ ima biyalẽ buk kori fiya anĩ yalen.  
\v 8 Sain ĩ anĩ yalen, ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo, mudur adodo tuwenti-fo geid, Sipsip Naal wagen kuku den. Idi mugu mugu harp\f + \fr 5:8  \ft Harp anĩ gita gen musik kodẽ dedig.\f* ado beĩ gol nem kaau sumeĩ biya isokoseya ado guri difen, kaau sumeĩ biya are momoiya tamo kayau neid kosẽ.  
\v 9 Age de fen, idi seg mata dalen:  
\q1 “Õ buk kori fiya anĩ wale fen,  
\q2 yogon ĩtãfiya uris sewen anĩ fara feleya kisi feleya bagai,  
\q1 ere nigin, õ dinõkesi di,  
\q2 õ ogon naud bunem  
\q2 ibor ganan bun, od fire fire ganan bun, tamo kayau ganan bun ado, teneub ganan bun, Negur nẽ tamo kayau na waledin.   
\q1
\v 10 Õ idi neda Negur aruna dalouf nigin, tano ado pris unenẽdin,  
\q2 ago di, idi teneub ganan lo fiya nigin mudur dibodõf.”   
\p
\v 11 Age de di, aya malau ara ken, engel musei bagai neid aiteid karĩ aun, idi tausen musei ado handred tausen musei wal fiya. Idi king nẽ sia, ereb mata ibodõya ado, mudur adodo salili difiyẽdin.  
\v 12 Age de fen, idi aiteid odugem seg dalen:  
\q1 “Sipsip Naal dukesin ĩ  
\q1 megeir, safina, kisi biya, totol, yana odug, fula fiya medeĩya ado,  
\q1 yana yaleseya yaleya kisi feleya bagai!”   
\p
\v 13 Agef fen, aya, ereb ereb ganan saa ilun difaref, tenebur difaref, teneub farumen difaref ado, maaĩ bun difaref, ereb ereb ganan anĩ namen mata difaref idi seg dale mog, karĩ aun:  
\q1 “Ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibodok ado Sipsip Naal bun,  
\q1 yana yaleseya, yana odug, fula fiya medeĩya ado, megeir,  
\q2 gai gai ibodkalauf!”   
\m
\v 14 Ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo diron, “Momoi,” age de di, mudur adodo kuku de fen, yana dalesen.   
\c 6  
\s1 Ĩtãfiya Uris  
\p
\v 1 Aya lo afe mog, Sipsip Naal ĩtãfiya uris sewen anĩ uyulil fara fen. Age fe di, aya, ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo takam, ait kolimei ait gen bun eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Usi!”  
\v 2 Aya lo afen, aya wageun an hos lalau taka ifaren. Tamo anĩ teten ibodon ĩ wi taka iroun, ĩ kusĩ wal fiya nẽ teter ifenen, age fe di, ĩ hos bun kusĩ wal fe fen, kusĩ wal fediyouf nigin ilen.   
\p
\v 3 Sipsip Naal ĩ ĩtãfiya uris uyulil dõ fiya anĩ fara fen, age fe di, aya ereb mata ibodõya uyulil dõ fiya anĩ eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Usi!”  
\v 4 Age ye di, hos taka isin, are giriya bagai. Tamo anĩ teten ibodon ĩ, tenebur tamal malol yalel fen, tamo abob didenkesiyouf nigin megeir ifenen. Ĩ anĩ dimig odug ifenen.   
\p
\v 5 Sipsip Naal ĩ ĩtãfiya uris anĩ dõ fiya fara fen, age fe di, aya ereb mata ibodõya anĩ dõ fiya anĩ eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Usi!” Aya lo afen, aya wageun an hos karos taka ifaren. Tamo anĩ teten ibodon, yogon ima bun ĩ foi fiya nẽ safina iroun.  
\v 6 Age fe di, aya ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo atun ait taka gen karĩ aun are iron, “Naa tekelei nẽ mala solo wit bret tekelei yalouf, naa tekelei nẽ mala solo baali bret towo yalouf. Ago fen, oliv moul ado wain to daũ wo!”   
\p
\v 7 Sipsip Naal ĩ ĩtãfiya uris anĩ dõ fiya fara fen, age fe di, aya ereb mata ibodõya anĩ dõ fiya anĩ eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Usi!”  
\v 8 Aya lo afen, aya wageun an hos bailuya taka ifaren. Tamo anĩ teten ibodon ĩ yana Laa, age fe di, Hades ĩ degẽ degẽ fiyen. Idi tenebur tamo kayau aiwa adodo foi fiya atun taka anĩ, dimig nem, kadir nem, dagi odug nem ado, tenebur gaar kuĩ nem didenkesiyouf nigin megeir ifenẽdin.   
\p
\v 9 Sipsip Naal ĩ ĩtãfiya uris anĩ dõ fiya fara fen, age fe di, aya idi Negur nẽ od dale fen, feseya sã od anĩ wogõ de di, didenkesin anidi neid meleidkanon alta farumen ailedin.  
\v 10 Idi aiteid odugem diweig diron, “Ereb ereb ganan nẽ Odug, fateul fen momoi, ere sain bun bagai, õ tenebur tamo kayau es woid fen, idi amã didenamakesin nigin mala solo wenẽdiyouf?”  
\v 11 Age de di, idi mugu mugu kolos lalau meluk ifenẽdin, agef fen, idi naal sain meluk tari de mog, dogo neid kabĩ tureid tar ado momoiya tamo kayau Negur igirnẽdin ganan, idi age difedin gen didenkesiya kisi falauf nigin irokenẽdin.   
\p
\v 12 Aya ĩ ĩtãfiya uris anĩ dõ fiya fara fel mog, ailen. Age fe di, mimĩ odug wõ yen. Gaa gugum kel fen, wau gudũ fiya nẽ gabar meme siwi nem iwaya gen karos kelen. Ogõ oditekei naud giriya gen falei felen.  
\v 13 Age fe di, saa ilun barisa tenebur kuku ren, are aa fig faat dobi yau totolem yoũ fe di, kuku redig gen age fen.  
\v 14 Saa, pepa kori fiya gen iwaikelen, agef fen, arei ganan ado nuyo ganan, dogo neid modoũ ditoraran.   
\p
\v 15 Age fe di, tenebur nẽ king, tamo yeneid adodo, kusĩ mudur, safina musei adodo, megeir adodo ado, ferfer ganan ado tamo kafĩ fiya sã bun difaref ganan, kuren ado arei nẽ sa atun diminanan.  
\v 16 Idi arei ado sa diweig dirokenẽdin, “Tetenaman kubũg fen, ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibodok anĩ nawa ado Sipsip Naal nẽ didi bun tamal unokolnamãg!  
\v 17 Ere nigin, idi neid didi nẽ naa odug mogo isin, anĩ nigin, aim ifareya kisi feleya?”   
\c 7  
\s1 Israel Tamo Kayau 144,000 Bun Uris Dinon  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya engel aiwa adodo, teneub idikeleya uyu uyu aiwa adodo bun, difar fen, teneub uyu uyu aiwa adodo nẽ yau, yau takam teneub be, maaĩ be, aa taka bun to fũ fouf nigin kafĩ difel mog, ailen.  
\v 2 Age afe fen, aya engel taka mata ibodõya Negur nẽ ĩtãfiya uris ado gaa iseyan ise mog, ailen. Ĩ engel aiwa adodo teneub ado maaĩ daũ fiya nẽ megeir ifenẽdin anidi, ait odugem iweig irokenẽdin:  
\v 3 “Ã teneub be, maaĩ be, aa taka fau mog to daũg, amã neda Negur nẽ ferfer demeid bun ĩtãfiya uris manol len.”  
\v 4 Age ye di, aya idi ĩtãfiya nẽ uris dinon anidi ganĩ anĩ karĩ aun, are 144,000 idi Israel ibor ganan bun temeleid.   
\q1
\v 5 Juda nẽ ibor bun tamal 12,000 are ĩtãfiya uris dinon,  
\q1 Ruben nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,  
\q1 Gad nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,   
\q1
\v 6 Aser nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,  
\q1 Naftali nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,  
\q1 Manase nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,   
\q1
\v 7 Simeon nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,  
\q1 Lewi nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,  
\q1 Isakar nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,   
\q1
\v 8 Sebulun nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,  
\q1 Josef nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000,  
\q1 Benjamin nẽ ibor bun tamal are 12,000.   
\s1 Guru Fiya Mala Odug Kolos Lalau Meluk Difonundin  
\p
\v 9 Anĩ bure fele di, aya lo afen, aya wageun an guru fiya mala odug bagai, taka nem iwesleya kisi feleya sã, idi teneub ganan bun, ibor ganan bun, tamo kayau ganan bun ado, od fire fire ganan bun temeleid, idi king nẽ sia wagen ado Sipsip Naal wagen difaren. Idi kolos lalau meluk difoun ken, pam boge anã boge gen anĩ imedim guri difen.  
\v 10 Age de fen, idi aiteid odugem diweig diron:  
\q1 “Kel gei fiya are  
\q1 neda Negur king nẽ sia bun ibodok ado  
\q1 Sipsip Naal nẽ.”   
\m
\v 11 Engel ganan, king nẽ sia ado, mudur adodo ado, ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo salili difiyeĩd difar fen, king nẽ sia wagen neweid lẽ kuku de fen, Negur yana dalesen.  
\v 12 Idi diron:  
\q1 “Momoi!  
\q1 Yana yaleseya, fula fiya medeĩya,  
\q1 kisi biya, de fiyẽya, yana odug,  
\q1 megeir ado, totol are  
\q1 neda Negur bun gai gai ibodkalauf.  
\q1 Momoi!”   
\p
\v 13 Age de di, mudur adodo takam aya to fiyan, “Idi eneidi kolos lalau meluk difonun are nanidim, idi nainenem disin?”   
\p
\v 14 Aya ĩ arokenen, “Tamo biya, õ keleĩ.”  
\p Age au di, ĩ irokanan, “Eneidi are darau, kafĩ fiya odug bun temeleid disin. Idi dogo neid kolos meluk Sipsip Naal naud nem kulo dife di, lalaun.  
\v 15 Anĩ nigin,  
\q1 “idi Negur nẽ king nẽ sia wagen difar fen,  
\q2 yogon tempel bun gaa ado bõ ganan aruna daledig.  
\q1 Age dife di, ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibodok anim yogon salafat biraraũ fe fen, kerũ fediyouf.   
\q1
\v 16 Idi baban to naũ fediyouf,  
\q2 to naan ail fediyouf.  
\q1 Gaam be, ereb uruwa adom,  
\q2 baban to isaĩnẽdiyouf.   
\q1
\v 17 Ere nigin, Sipsip Naal king nẽ sia atun ifaref inim, dogo neid lo fiya tamo ibodõf.  
\q2 Ĩ idi mata ibodõya nẽ naan warur bun gurif iroulediyouf.  
\q1 Age fe di, Negur ĩ idi meleid bun tamal maruid ganan waĩ falauf.”   
\c 8  
\s1 Ĩtãfiya Uris Namba Sewen Ado Aa Gaula Sumeĩ Biya Nẽ Gol Beĩ  
\p
\v 1 Sain Sipsip Naal ĩtãfiya uris namba sewen anĩ fara fele di, saa ilun hap aua age fiya karasã sã mutũ bagai yenen.   
\p
\v 2 Age fe di, aya engel sewen Negur wagen difaren anidi, taur sewen ifeneĩd mog, ailen.   
\p
\v 3 Engel taka ĩ, aa gaula sumeĩ biya nẽ gol beĩ ado isi, alta bun ifaren. Ĩ aa gaula sumeĩ biya musei, momoiya tamo kayau ganan neid kosẽ ado, king nẽ sia wagen gol alta bun sesewi fouf nigin difenen.\fig Aa gaula sumeĩ biya nẽ gol beĩ.|src="hk00268c.tif" size="span" ref="8:3" \fig*  
\v 4 Aa gaula sumeĩ biya nẽ kaau, momoiya tamo kayau neid kosẽ ado, engel ima bun tamal Negur wagen iselen.  
\v 5 Agef fen, engel aa gaula sumeĩ biya nẽ beĩ yale, alta bun tamal yã ife fen, tenebur iran, age fe di, kolimei gudũya, gurũya odug, kolimei filiya ado, mimĩ wõ yen.   
\s1 Taur  
\p
\v 6 Age fe di, engel sewen taur sewen ado, taur wese fiya nigin dodok difen.   
\p
\v 7 Engel uyulil yogon taur wese fe di, uyẽ ais, yã naud ado bagu fen, isi di, tenebur iraran, age fe di, teneub tekelei faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka adok isaikelen, aa ganan faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka adok isaikelen, agef fen, fisir mata ganan isasaikelen.   
\p
\v 8 Engel uyu wõ yen anĩ dõ fiya yogon taur wese fe di, ereb arei odug gen yã fitotoleya ado maaĩwõ iran. Maaĩ faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka, naud falei felen,  
\v 9 maaĩwõ ereb ereb mata ibodõya faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka gare den, agef fen, waag ganan faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka daũ felen.   
\p
\v 10 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka yogon taur wese fe di, barisa odug yal gen kaur fen, saa ilunem, naan faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka bun ado, naan warur anidi bun kubũ yen.  
\v 11 Barisa anĩ nẽ yana Dirikeĩ. Naan faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka dirikeĩ kele di, tamo kayau musei, naan dirikeĩ kelen anĩ bunem gare den.   
\p
\v 12 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka yogon taur wese fe di, gaa faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka, ogõ faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka ado, barisa faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka yũ di, idi ganan faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka gugum kelen. Naa faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka lalan sa kelen, agef fen, bõ faraf towo fiya gen anĩ takag age fen.   
\p
\v 13 Aya lo afe mog, aya webi taka karĩ au mog, ilun fatutu ye fen, ait odugem iweig iron, “Malalon! Malalon! Malalon tenebur dibodok anidi bun, ere nigin, engel towog mogo taur ait wese difou fenẽ!”   
\c 9  
\p
\v 1 Engel anĩ dõ fiya engel taka yogon taur wese fe di, aya barisa taka saa ilunem tenebur kubũ yen anĩ ailen. Barisa are ku isil idĩya sã nẽ ki anĩ ifenen.  
\v 2 Ĩ ku isil idĩya sã anĩ kã fele di, kaau are yã odug kũ fiya modoũ bun tamal gen fã yen. Ku isil idĩya sã bun tamal kaau anim, gaa ado saa gugum kelen.  
\v 3 Age fe di, kaau namen tamal, totobi tenebur wowã den, are idi neid megeir, tenebur ãbei neid megeir gen ifenẽdin.  
\v 4 Idi tenebur tamal fisir be, ereb aayũ be, aa taka to daũ difouf, anĩ ere, tamo kayau idi Negur nẽ uris demeid bun sã anidi dogol daũ difediyouf nigin irokenẽdin.  
\v 5 Idi tamo idenkesiya nẽ megeir to ifenẽdin, anĩ ere, idi ogõ faif bun darau dogol difenẽdiyouf nigin megeir ifenẽdin. Age fe di, idi neid darau arar, ãbei tamo garũ fe di, darau arar iledig gen.  
\v 6 Naa anidi bun tamo laa dimirẽf, anĩ ere, to dilouf. Idi laa orodiyouf, anĩ ere, laa to gurug fediyouf.   
\p
\v 7 Totobi are hos kusĩ bun ileya nẽ gegen. Idi neid mudureid bun, ereb gol teter gen kurũ difedin, idi neid neweid tamo neweid gen.  
\v 8 Nedi fatiyeid kayau fatiyeid gen, agef fen, waileid are laion waila gen.  
\v 9 Nedi siot kapa are ain nẽ siot kapa gen, agef fen, idi neid wayeid furũya are hos musei ado karis kusĩ bun gududu de fen, gou redig gen.\fig Hos musei ado karis kusĩ bun gudur fen, gou redig.|src="hk00191c.tif" size="span" ref="9:9" \fig*  
\v 10 Idi ibud ado waileid ãbei neid gen, agef fen, idi ibud nem ogõ faif bun tamo kayau darau difenẽdiyouf nigin megeir adon.  
\v 11 Idi uyu iroukenẽdiya nẽ king ado, are ku isil idĩya sã nẽ engel, in yana Hibru od nem are Abadon, Grik od nem are Apolion.\f + \fr 9:11  \ft Abadon ado Apolion nẽ gariya, Daũ Fiya Tamo.\f*   
\p
\v 12 Morõ odug uyulil anĩ bure felen, age fe di, morõ odug uru are fau disif.   
\p
\v 13 Engel namba sigis anĩ yogon taur wese fe di, aya ait taka gol alta Negur wagen ifaref anĩ nẽ karat aiwa adodo bunem wowã yeid mog, karĩ aun.  
\v 14 Ait are engel namba sigis taur ado anĩ irokenen, “Engel aiwa adodo Yufretis naan odug bun difofan anidi fara woidle.”  
\v 15 Age ye di, engel aiwa adodo are aua, naa, ogõ, yar enei bun bagai, tamo teneub ganan bun fara fiya towo anĩ taka adok didenkesiyouf nigin, dodok fedin anĩ folõ feledin.  
\v 16 Hos teten kusĩ bun ileya nẽ tamo anidi are 200 milion. Aya dogo neid namba karĩ aun.   
\p
\v 17 Aya malau seleulã kurã fiya bun, hos adodo tamo hos tetedin dibodon anidi eig fiya ailedin: Idi neid siot kapa are, yã giriya gen, maaĩ gegẽ gen ado, bailuya salfa gen. Hos mudureid are, laion mudureid gen, agef fen, idi eweid bunem yã, kaau ado, salfa wowã yen.  
\v 18 Tamo tenebur ganan faraf towo fiya gen anĩ taka ganan, sane towo anim, yã, kaau ado, salfa idi eweid bun wowã yen anim didenkesin.  
\v 19 Hos idi neid megeir are eweid bun ado ibud bun ibodon, ere nigin, idi neid ibud are gogour gen fen, mudureid anim tamo kayau darau difenẽdidig.   
\p
\v 20 Tamo kayau tunĩ ganan, sane eneidim to didenkesin anidi, idi imedim dinon anĩ to ditor ken, waud to falei yen. Idi kaa sesen yeneid yaleseya to ditor ken, gol, silwa, bras, meein ado, aa nẽ idegẽya waitou, are lo fiya, karĩya be, iyõya kisi felya sã anidi yeneid yaleseya itorõya sã.  
\v 21 Idi tamo yukesiya, dogo neid idegẽya kosẽya, dogo neid noli tobonunã be, dogo neid bẽ yaleya tobonunã nigineg waud to falei yen.   
\c 10  
\s1 Engel Ado Buk Kori Fiya Naal  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya engel megeir ado taka saa ilunem isi mog, ailen. Ĩ lalom silef fen, yogon mudur bun walol ado. In nawa gaa gen, agef fen, yogon ye are tor yã bobo reya gen.  
\v 2 Ĩ buk kori fiya naal taka ima bun fara feleya iroun. Ĩ ye biyalẽ maaĩ bun iten ken, ye kilẽ teneub bun itenen.  
\v 3 Agef fen, ĩ laion ninirã ye gen ken, ait odugem iweig iron. Sain ĩ iwegin, kolimei gudũya sewen neid aiteid wogõ den.  
\v 4 Kolimei gudũya sewen wogõ de di, aya anĩ atotau fenẽ age afen, anĩ ere, aya ait taka saa ilunem eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Ereb kolimei gudũya sewen wogõ den anĩ bun ĩtãfiya uris uno fen, õ to utotauf.”   
\p
\v 5 Age ye di, engel maaĩ bun ado teneub bun ifar mog ailen, are ima biyalẽ saa ilun yalesen.  
\v 6 Agef fen, engel ĩ, Negur gai gai mata ibodkeleya, saa ado ereb ereb ganan anĩ bun difaref, teneub ado ereb ereb ganan anĩ bun difaref, maaĩ ado ereb ereb ganan anĩ bun difaref inodin anĩ yana nem, wau kuturol fen, iron, “Foiya nẽ sain sã!  
\v 7 Anĩ ere, engel namba sewen anĩ yogon taur wese fouf naa bun, Negur nẽ waa, ĩ yogon ferfer profet irokenẽdin kilei, agef wõ ye kisi falauf.”   
\p
\v 8 Anĩ bure fele di, ait saa ilunem aya irokana di, karĩ aun, are baban irokanan, “Ule, engel maaĩ ado teneub bun ifaref anĩ ima bun, buk kori fiya fara feleya irouf anĩ wale,” yen.   
\p
\v 9 Age ye di, aya engel garan ele fen, buk kori fiya naal anĩ ifanauf nigin arokenen. Ĩ aya irokanan, “Are wale wõ wakas. Are õ namẽ bun dirikeĩ youf, anĩ ere, õ awã bun are nin te gen dan yõf.”  
\v 10 Aya buk kori fiya naal engel ima bun tamal ale on. Are neu awau bun nin te gen dan fiyan, anĩ ere, aya akalaisile di, nameun dirikeĩ fiyan.  
\v 11 Age afe di, idi aya dirokanan, “Õ tamo kayau musei, teneub musei, od musei ado, king musei nigin, baban profet od wogõ wouf.”   
\c 11  
\s1 Od Megeir Fiya Nẽ Isennẽya Tamo Uru  
\p
\v 1 Aya sisi fiya nẽ tibog gen werĩ taka ifana fen, irokanan, “Ule fen, Negur nẽ tempel ado alta sisi wo fen, Negur yana an ganim dalesedig anĩ uwes.  
\v 2 Anĩ ere, tempel fofomala anĩ utor. Are to sisi wo, ere nigin, are haiden ifenẽdin. Idi foti-tu ogõ bun taun fateul anĩ lai difalauf.  
\v 3 Age dife di, aya neu od megeir fiya nẽ isennẽya tamo uru megeir afenẽdi di, idi 1,260 naa anidi bun wau gudũ fiya nẽ gabar difoun ken, profet od kurõ difesiyouf.”  
\v 4 Eneidi are oliv aa uru ado lam tutur uru, tenebur nẽ Odug wagen difaref.  
\v 5 Takam idi darau ifenẽdiya nigin age fouf are, yã eweid bunem wõ ye fen, idi neid kiwai tar oditekei yakur falauf. Aibem taka idi darau ifenẽdiyou fenẽ age fouf, are agef laa fouf bagai.  
\v 6 Tamo eneidi saa katĩ feleya nẽ megeir ado nigin, idi profet od wogõ douf sain, uyẽ to isiyouf, agef fen, idi naan falei fe di, naud wõya nigin megeir ado fen, ereb sain orodif kilei, idi ereb sane fire fire bunem teneub yũya nẽ megeir ado.   
\p
\v 7 Idi Negur nẽ od kurõ fesiya bure difele di, gaar kuĩ anĩ ku isil idĩya sã bunem ulõ yeis fen, idi geid kusĩ de, wal feid fen, idenkesiyouf.  
\v 8 Idi neid bouweid buru taun odug anĩ nẽ naabur yenẽf, taun are yaab od bunem Sodom ado Isip dedig, an nedi Odugeg aa tetek bun dukesin.  
\v 9 Tamo kayau fire fire bun tamal, ibor fire fire bun tamal, od fire fire bun tamal ado, teneub fire fire bun tamal, tamo kayau idi, naa towo ado naa taka atun bun, nedi bouweid buru dile fen, mumã difouf nigin to yo douf.  
\v 10 Tamo kayau tenebur dibodok anidi, idi nigin waud al fe di, sifa dino fen, idi abob safina ege luwa difenẽf, ere nigin, profet uru eneidi, idi tenebur dibodok anidi darau difenẽdin.   
\p
\v 11 Anĩ ere, naa towo ado naa taka atun anĩ bure fele di, mata neseya nẽ uur Negur bunem idi namedin ilen, age fe di, idi fafã de difaren. Age dife di, idi diledin are kumĩ tererẽ den.  
\v 12 Anĩ bure fele di, idi saa ilunem ait odug eig ye irokeneĩd mog, karĩ den, “Ilun ein useg,” yen. Age ye di, idi neid kiwai lo difeid mog, idi lalo bunem saa ilun diselen.   
\p
\v 13 Sain anĩ bun bagai, mimĩ odug wõ ye di, taun anĩ bun ten tekelei adok daũ felen. Sewen tausen tamo kayau mimĩ anim idenkesin. Age fe di, idi gareya sã are kumĩ tererẽ de fen, saa ilun nẽ Negur fula fiya medeĩya difenen.   
\p
\v 14 Morõ odug uyu ilen anĩ dõ fiya bure fele di, morõ odug anĩ dõ fiya mogo melsã bagai isiyou fenẽ.   
\s1 Engel Taur Namba Sewen Anĩ Wese Fen  
\p
\v 15 Engel namba sewen anĩ yogon taur wese fe di, saa ilun ait odug wowã ye fen, diron:  
\q1 “Tenebur nẽ tano are, neda Odug ado yogon Kristus nẽ tano wõ yen,  
\q2 age fe di, ĩ gai gai lo fiya nigin anĩ nẽ mudur ibodõf.”   
\m
\v 16 Age de di, tuwenti-fo mudur adodo, Negur wagen dogo neid king nẽ sia bun dibodon wageidlẽ kuku de fen, Negur yana dales,  
\v 17 diron:  
\q1 “Odug Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri weid uyu uroudig anĩ,  
\q2 õ gama ubodok, kulu ubodon, amã õ de mayok,  
\q1 ere nigin, õ ogon megeir odug wale fen,  
\q2 lo fiya nigin king wõ won.   
\q1
\v 18 Teneub ganan waud sanen, anĩ ere, ogon didi mogo isin.  
\q1 Tamo gare den anĩ es fediya sain mogo isin,  
\q2 ogon ferfer profet, ogon tamo kayau fateul ado,  
\q1 idi ogon yanã nigin anini den anidi nanaal ado odudug,  
\q2 mala solo ifenẽdiya sain mogo isin,  
\q1 idi teneub daũ difef anidi daũ fediya sain mogo isin.”   
\p
\v 19 Anĩ bure fele di, Negur nẽ tempel saa ilun kã fele di, yogon tempel namen yogon bar itenẽya nẽ bogis wõ yen. Age fe di, kolimei filiya, gurũya odug, kolimei gudũya, mimĩ ado, uyẽ ais ado odug wõ yen.   
\c 12  
\s1 Kayau Ado Gogour Odug  
\p
\v 1 Uris odug fire bagai saa ilun wõ yen. Kayau taka gaa ifoun kel fen, yogon ye farumen ogolam ado, yogon mudur bun barisa tuwelf nẽ teter kurũ fen.  
\v 2 Ĩ bou ado fen, kesu gõ fiya sain melsã di, darau nigin kaĩ yen.  
\v 3 Age fe di, uris takag saa ilun wõ yen. Gogour giriya odug bagai mudur sewen, karat ten ado, teter sewen mudur sewen bun difaren ado wõ yen. \fig Gogour giriya odug bagai mudur sewen, karat ten ado, teter sewen mudur sewen bun difaren ado.|src="Boyd-dragon.tif" size="span" ref="12:3" \fig*  
\v 4 Yogon ibum barisa fara fiya towo anĩ taka saa ilun waĩf, tenebur iraran. Gogour odug anĩ kayau kesu gõ fiya sain melsã anĩ wagen ifaren, are ĩ yogon kesu gõ falaisi di, itobouf nigin age fen.  
\v 5 Kayau kesu taka gõ fen, are kesu monog, ĩ teneub ganan ain manig nem ulum irokenẽdiyouf. Age fe di, yogon kesu kaisã bagai gurar fe yale, Negur ado yogon king nẽ sia wagen irouselen.  
\v 6 Kayau, Negurem modoũ dodok fenen nẽ gerere tuan iya ilen, an ĩ Negurem 1,260 naa kulatun fiyẽf.   
\p
\v 7 Agef fen, saa ilun kusĩ wõ yen. Maikel yogon engel geid, gogour odug geid kusĩ den. Age fe di, gogour odug, yogon engel geid, abag idi geid kusĩ den.  
\v 8 Anĩ ere, gogour odug in engel geid, idi neid megeir kisi feleya sã, anĩ nigin, idi saa ilun nedi modoũ ditoron.  
\v 9 Gogour odug bagai are dale diran, are gogour kulu tamal bagai, anĩ Devil be, Satan dedig, ĩ teneub ganan idegnẽdidig. Ĩ tenebur dale dira ken, yogon engeleg ĩ geid diraran.   
\p
\v 10 Age fe di, aya saa ilunem ait odug eig ye mog, karĩ aun:  
\q1 “Gama neda Negur nẽ kel yaleya, megeir, tano ado,  
\q2 yogon Kristus nẽ totol mogo isin.  
\q1 Ere nigin, ĩ neda turada tar bouweid yũya od irõdig,  
\q2 ĩ neda Negur wagen, gaa ado bõ, idi bouweid yũya od irõdig,  
\q2 are mogo dale diran.   
\q1
\v 11 Idi Sipsip Naal naud bunem ado,  
\q2 dogo neid Jesus nigin od wogõya bunem  
\q2 ĩ wal difiyen.  
\q1 Idi dogo mata ibodõya nigin kisi fatuk to dale fen,  
\q2 laa uyu ditoron.   
\q1
\v 12 Anĩ nigin, saa ilun õ ado,  
\q2 an ufaregef ã, wauĩ kulĩ ye!  
\q1 Anĩ ere, teneub ado maaĩ ã, meleĩlon ado,  
\q2 ere nigin, Satan mogo ã bun isilen!  
\q1 Seye ĩ bun isokosef,  
\q2 ere nigin, ĩ keleĩ, yogon sain mogo modegef.”   
\p
\v 13 Sain gogour odug ĩ tenebur diran anĩ ile fen, ĩ kayau kesu monog gõ fen anĩ iruf ilen.  
\v 14 Kayau are, gerere tuan modoũ ĩ nigin dodok fenen anĩ bun fatutu ye ilauf nigin, webi odug nẽ waye uru difenen, an kayau gogour odug anim to irounẽf nigin, yar towo ado yar taka atun, kayau anĩ kulatun difiyẽf.  
\v 15 Age fe di, gogour ĩ awa kurenem, naan odug gen, naan foula fen, are kayau anĩ wal fiye ken, kuwei bun yale irousilauf nigin age fen.  
\v 16 Anĩ ere, teneub kayau isenne ken, awa aã ye fen, gogour odug awa kurenem naan odug foula fen anĩ yakasin.  
\v 17 Age fe di, gogour odug kayau nigin fatuk bagai name fen, kayau nẽ ibor tar fau dibodok anidi ganan geid kusĩya nigin ilen, idi Negur nẽ ĩtãfiya dõ de fen, Jesus nẽ biya od dirouf anidi.   
\c 13  
\p
\v 1 Agef fen, gogour odug maaĩ yerin ifaren.  
\s1 Gaar Kuĩ Maaĩ Namenem Ulõ Yesin  
\p Age fe di, aya gaar kuĩ taka maaĩ namenem ulõ yeis mog, ailen. Ĩ karat ten ado, mudur sewen ado fen, ĩ yogon karat ten bun teter adodo fen, mudur ganan bun Negur kono fiya nẽ yana ado.  
\v 2 Gaar kuĩ aya ailen are lepat\f + \fr 13:2  \ft Lepat are fus kuĩ odug gen.\f* gen, anĩ ere, yogon ye are bea nẽ ye gegen, agef fen, awa laion nẽ gen. Gogour odug yogon megeir, yogon king nẽ sia ado, totol odug, gaar kuĩ ifenen.\fig Bea.|src="lb00048c.tif" size="span" ref="13:2" \fig*  
\v 3 Gaar kuĩ nẽ mudur taka are dũ di, laa fou fenẽ gen yenen, anĩ ere, dũ di, laa fou fenẽ gen yenen are baban biya len. Teneub ganan terẽ de fen, gaar kuĩ dõ difen.  
\v 4 Tamo idi gogour odug yana dalesen, ere nigin, ĩ gaar kuĩ megeir ifenen. Age de fen, idi gaar kuĩg yana dales fen, diron, “Aim anĩ gaar kuĩ gen? Aim anĩ ĩ ado kusĩ yalesauf?”   
\p
\v 5 Gaar kuĩ ĩ, yogo seli kulõ fiya nẽ od ado Negur nigin kono fiya nẽ od wogõ youf nigin sigor ifen ken, foti-tu ogõ bun kabĩ yalouf nigin megeir ifenen.  
\v 6 Gaar kuĩ ĩ Negur kono fiyẽf nigin, Negur yana, Negur nẽ ibodõya modoũ ado, idi saa ilun dibodok anidi bun bou yũya od wogõ youf nigin awa kamen.  
\v 7 Gaar kuĩ ĩ, Negur nẽ tamo kayau geid kusĩ de fen, idi wal fediyouf nigin megeir ifenen. Agef fen, ĩ, ibor ganan, tamo kayau ganan, od fire fire ganan ado, teneub ganan nẽ mudur ibodõf nigin megeir ifenen.  
\v 8 Tenebur dibodok anidi ganan gaar kuĩ yana dalesauf, are idi, saa teneub ado kare fen sain bunem isi sain enei bun, idi yeneid Sipsip Naal dukesin anĩ nẽ mata ibodõya nẽ buk bun to itoton anidim age difouf.   
\p
\v 9 Taka ĩ weder adouf, utornẽg len, ĩ karĩ youf.   
\q1
\v 10 Taka ĩ kalabus bun ileya nigin igirnẽf,  
\q2 ĩ kalabus bun ilauf.  
\q1 Taka ĩ dimig nem dukesiyouf nigin igirnẽf,  
\q2 dimig nem ĩ dukesiyouf.  
\m Enei wõ youf sain bun, Negur nẽ tamo kayau feseya sã totol difar fen, momoiya kafĩ difel dirouwauf.   
\s1 Gaar Kuĩ Teneb Bunem Ulõ Yesen  
\p
\v 11 Anĩ bure fele di, gaar kuĩ taka teneburem ulõ yeis mog, ailen. Ĩ sipsip naal gen karat uru ado, anĩ ere, ĩ gogour odug gen wogõ yedig.  
\v 12 Ĩ gaar kuĩ uyulil ulõ yesin anĩ lof mog, yogon megeir ganan yale fen, kabĩ yalen. Agef fen, ĩ, teneub ado idi tenebur difaref anidi ganan, gaar kuĩ uyulil ulõ yesin, are dũ di, laa fou fenẽ gen yenen anĩ baban biya len, ĩ yana dalesauf nigin nugo fedin.  
\v 13 Agef fen, ĩ uris memelik odug inodin, ĩ tamo kayau lo de mog, age fe di, yã saa ilunem tenebur isin anĩg age fen.  
\v 14 Ĩ gaar kuĩ uyulil ulõ yesin anĩ lof mog, megeir yale fen, memelik inodin nigin, ĩ tenebur difaref anidi idegnẽdin. Ĩ, gaar kuĩ, are dimig nem dũ di, baban biya len anĩ yana dalesauf nigin, idi anĩ nẽ malakanon dinouf nigin irokenẽdin.  
\v 15 Ĩ gaar kuĩ uyulil ulõ yesin anĩ malakanon mata ifenẽya nẽ megeir ifenen, anĩ bunem, malakanon are sã wogõ yen, ĩ age fe di, idi malakanon anĩ yana yaleseya ditoron anidi ganan didenkesin.  
\v 16 Gaar kuĩ dumen ulõ yesin are, tamo kayau ganan, nanaal ado odudug, safina ado ado maleg, kafĩ fiya sã tamo ado ferfer, uris taka imeid biyalẽ be, demeid bun dalouf nigin nugo fedin.  
\v 17 Age fe di, aibem taka to na yale fen, to na sur fouf, ĩ gaar kuĩ nẽ uris adouf anĩ dogol, uris are gaar kuĩ nẽ yana be, yogo yana nẽ namba.   
\p
\v 18 Kisi biya adouf are, enei keleĩ youf. Are taka ĩ karĩya biya adouf, ĩ utornẽg len, gaar kuĩ nẽ namba iwesauf, ere nigin, namba are tamo nẽ. In namba are 666.   
\c 14  
\s1 Sipsip Naal Ado 144,000 Tamo  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya lo afen, aya wageun Sipsip Naal Saion Arei bun 144,000, yogon yana ado yogon tama nẽ yana demeid bun itotoyan anidi, ĩ geid difaren.  
\v 2 Age afe fen, aya ait taka saa ilunem, naan fatuk wĩ ye fen, gou redig gen ado, kolimei gudũya odug gen karĩ aun. Ait aya karĩ aun are, harp kodẽya tamo harp kodẽ dedig gen.  
\v 3 Age de fen, idi, king nẽ sia, ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo ado, mudur adodo wagedin seg mata dalen. Aibem taka seg anĩ keleĩya kisi feleya sã, 144,000 idi tenebur tamal kel gei fedin anidim dogol.  
\v 4 Eneidi are kayau geid yen ken, amuyẽ inoya sã anidi, ere nigin, idi dogo nigin karẽtut bagai dibodon. Idi Sipsip Naal narib ile di, idi dõ de diyõdig. Idi tamo ganan atun kel geif fen, faat uyulil yũya gen, Negur ado Sipsip Naal bun sesewi fedin.  
\v 5 Idi sigoredin idegẽya taka to wõ yen, idi bouweid bun od taka sã.   
\s1 Engel Towo  
\p
\v 6 Anĩ bure fele di, aya engel taka ilun bagai fatutu ye mog, ailen. Ĩ idi tenebur dibodok anidi, are teneub ganan, ibor ganan, od fire fire ganan ado, tamo kayau ganan bun kurõ fesiyouf nigin, mata ibodkeleya nẽ biya od ado ailen.  
\v 7 Ĩ ait odugem iron, “Negur anini wiyẽg fen, ĩ fula fiya medeĩya wenẽg, ere nigin, yogon es fiya nẽ sain mogo isin. Ĩ saa, teneub, maaĩ ado, naan warur inodin anĩ yana waleseg.”   
\p
\v 8 Anĩ dõ fiya engel takam dõ fiye ken, iron, “Ĩ kubũ yen! Babilon Odug kubũ yen, ĩ teneub ganan yogon seseirã tobonunã nẽ wain totol ifeneĩd don.”   
\p
\v 9 Anĩ dõ fiya engel takam dõ fiyeĩd fen, ait odugem iron, “Taka ĩ gaar kuĩ ado yogon malakanon yana yales fen, yogon uris dama bun be, ima bun yalouf,  
\v 10 ĩg Negur nẽ didi nẽ wain yãf, are mogo totol adok yogon didi nẽ kap bun fi felen. Ĩ engel fateul anidi ado Sipsip Naal meleid bun, salfa yã bobo reya bun darau yalouf.  
\v 11 Age fe di, dogo neid darau nẽ yãkaau fã ye, gai gai agef ibodkalauf. Idi gaar kuĩ ado yogon malakanon yana dalesedig anidi be, aib taka yogon yana nẽ uris yalen ĩ, naa be bõ, si inoya nẽ sain sã.”  
\v 12 Enei wõ youf sain bun, Negur nẽ tamo kayau, idi Negur nẽ ĩtãfiya dõ de fen, Jesus nigin momoiya dirou kafĩ difelef anidi, feseya sã megeir difarauf bagai.   
\p
\v 13 Anĩ bure fele di, aya saa ilunem ait taka eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Utot: Idi sain enei bunem ilauf ganan, Odug bun gare douf are el fediyouf.”  
\p Awa Uurem irok, “Momoi, idi dogo neid kabĩ bun si dinouf, ere nigin, idi ereb age difen are ado dilauf.”   
\s1 Tenebur Saaf Kusu Fiya Sain  
\p
\v 14 Aya lo afen, aya wageun lalo lalau taka ado, lalo bun ibodon are ‘tamo naal gen,’\f + \fr 14:14  \ft Daniel 7:13\f* ĩ yogon mudur bun gol teter kurũ fen, yogon ima bun dimig gunõ waila ado irouf anĩ ailen.  
\v 15 Age fe di, engel taka tempel bunem isi fen, ĩ lalo bun ibodon anĩ ait odugem iweig irokenen, “Ogon dimig gunõ waila ado wale fen, kokour wo, ere nigin, kokour fiya nẽ sain mogo isin, tenebur saaf kusu fiya nẽ are mogo mayol.”  
\v 16 Age ye di, lalo bun ibodon ĩ, yogon dimig gunõ waila ado tenebur waĩ fe di, tenebur saaf kokour fen.   
\p
\v 17 Engel taka, saa ilun oun tempel bunem isin, ĩg dimig gunõ waila ado iroun.  
\v 18 Age fe di, engel takag, yã lo fedig anĩ alta bunem isi fen, ait odugem ĩ dimig gunõ waila ado iroun anĩ iweig irokenen, “Ogon dimig gunõ waila ado wale fen, tenebur tamal wain nẽ biya kuru wo, ere nigin, wain biya are mayol.”\fig Wain nẽ biya ado dimig gunõ waila ado.|src="SIL-sickle.png" size="col" ref="14:18" \fig*  
\v 19 Engel ĩ yogon dimig gunõ waila ado anĩ tenebur waĩf fen, wain biya kuru fen, agef fen, ĩ Negur nẽ didi nẽ wain asi fiya modoũ odug bun iraran.  
\v 20 Wain biya are, taun yerin wain asi fiya modoũ bun asi difen, age dife di, naud wain asi fiya modoũ bunem isin, are 300 kilomita meluk fen, wan ado hap mita ilun.   
\c 15  
\s1 Engel Sewen Teneub Daũ Fiya Nẽ Sesen Sewen Adodo  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya saa ilun uris odug taka fire bagai ailen. Are engel sewen, idikeleya nẽ teneub daũ fiya nẽ sesen sewen adodo, are idi idikeleya nẽ, ere nigin, idi bunem Negur nẽ didi idikalauf.  
\v 2 Age afe fen, aya ereb taka maaĩ galas nem dinon anĩ, yã ado bagu fiya gen ail fen, idi gaar kuĩ, yogon malakanon ado, yogon yana nẽ namba kusĩ bun wal difen anidi, maaĩ yerin difaren anĩ ailen. Idi Negurem harp ifenẽdin anĩ guri de fen,  
\v 3 Negur nẽ ferfer, Moses nẽ seg ado, Sipsip Naal nẽ seg dalen:  
\q1 “Odug Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri weid uyu uroudig anĩ,  
\q2 õ agodig anĩ odug fen, mala yũ yaleya.  
\q1 Teneub ganan nẽ King,  
\q2 ogon naab are madur fen, momoi bagai.   
\q1
\v 4 O Odug, aim anĩ õ to kumĩ yo ken,  
\q2 õ yanã bun fula fiya medeĩya to inouf?  
\q1 Ere nigin, õ dogol fateul.  
\q1 Ogon tobonunã biya madur bagai are yaor won nigin,  
\q2 teneub ganan disi fen,  
\q1 õ wagen yanã dalesauf.”   
\p
\v 5 Anĩ bure fele di, aya lo afe mog, saa ilun oun tempel, Negur nẽ Od Kurõ Fesiya nẽ Salafat Fateul, are kã fen.  
\v 6 Tempel namenem, engel sewen idi teneub daũ fiya nẽ sesen sewen adodo anĩ ulõ desin. Idi kolos lalau amuyẽ sã, medeĩya difoun ken, idi akoreid bun gol let gu difedin.  
\v 7 Age dife di, ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo takam, gol beĩ sewen Negur mata faimud ibodkeleya nẽ didi isokoseya anĩ, engel sewen ifenẽdin.  
\v 8 Age fe di, tempel are, Negur nẽ fula fiya medeĩya ado yogon megeir nẽ kaau isokose di, engel sewen neid teneub daũ fiya nẽ sesen sewen anĩ fau bure feleya sã mog, taka nem tempel namen ileya kisi feleya sã.   
\c 16  
\s1 Beĩ Sewen Negur Nẽ Didi Ado  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya ait odug taka tempel bunem engel sewen irokeneĩd fen, eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Uleg, beĩ sewen Negur nẽ didi adodo anidi teneub bun fi weleg.”  
\v 2 Engel uyulil ile fen, yogon beĩ teneub bun fi fele di, guruma sane darau odug bagai anĩ, tamo kayau gaar kuĩ nẽ uris ado fen, yogon malakanon yana dalesedig anidi bun, wowã yen.   
\p
\v 3 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka, yogon beĩ maaĩ bun fi fele di, maaĩ anĩ laa tamo nẽ naud gen falei fen, age fe di, ereb ereb maaĩwõ mata dibodon ganan gare den.   
\p
\v 4 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka, yogon beĩ, naan odudug ado naan warur anidi bun fi felen, age fe di, naud falei feledin.  
\v 5 Age fe di, aya engel naan lo fedig anĩ eig ye mog, karĩ aun:  
\q1 “Õ gama ubodok, kulu ubodon, õ Fateul Bagai,  
\q2 õ madur bagai,  
\q2 ere nigin, õ mogo ago es won.   
\q1
\v 6 Idi ogon tamo kayau ado ogon profet didenkeis fen, dogo neid naud fi difelen,  
\q2 anĩ nigin, õ idi naud yõya nigin wenẽdin, are idi yõya kisin bagai wenẽdin.”   
\m
\v 7 Age ye di, aya alta eig ye mog, karĩ aun:  
\q1 “Momoi, Odug Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri weid uyu uroudig anĩ,  
\q2 ogon es fiya are, momoi fen madur bagai.”   
\p
\v 8 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka, yogon beĩ gaa bun fi fele di, gaa tamo kayau yã nem ifalegnẽdiyouf nigin megeir ifenen.  
\v 9 Idi uruwa totol bagai bunem ifalegnẽdi di, idi, Negur teneub daũ fiya nẽ sesen eneidi lo fedidig anĩ, yana kono difen, age de fen, idi waud falei ye fen, Negur yana yaleseya ditoron.   
\p
\v 10 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka, yogon beĩ gaar kuĩ nẽ king nẽ sia bun fi fele di, yogon tano gugum kelen. Tamo idi darau nigin baleid mũ de fen,  
\v 11 dogo neid darau ado gurumeid nigin, saa ilun nẽ Negur kono difen. Anĩ ere, idi ereb sane age difen anĩ to ditor ken, waud to falei yen.   
\p
\v 12 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka, yogon beĩ Yufretis naan odug bun fi fele di, naan are, gaa iseyan tamal king disiyouf nẽ naab dodok fiya nigin, gere kelen.  
\v 13 Anĩ bure fele di, aya kaa sesen towo felĩ gen, idi gogour odug awa kurem, gaar kuĩ awa kurem ado, idegẽya profet awa kurem ulõ deis mog, ailen.  
\v 14 Idi kaa sesen nẽ uur anidim memelik nẽ uris dino fen, idi teneub ganan nẽ king ganan bun dile fen, Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri feid uyu iroudig anĩ nẽ naa odug bun, idi kusĩ bun guru difouf nigin gou difediyouf.   
\p
\v 15 Jesus irok, “Lo welegei, aya bẽ tamo gen asiyouf! Taka ĩ mulaĩ yenẽya sa ken, yogon kolos sirin ado ibodok are, ĩ el fiyek, ere nigin, ĩ gemũ to ile di, yogon mama to dilouf.”   
\p
\v 16 Age de fen, idi king, Hibru od nem Amagedon dedig nẽ an guru difouf nigin gou difedin.   
\p
\v 17 Anĩ dõ fiya engel taka, yogon beĩ ilun owõbẽ fi fele di, tempel namenem king nẽ sia bunem ait odug wõ ye fen, iron, “Gama mogo bure felef!”  
\v 18 Age fe di, kolimei filiya, gurũya odug, kolimei gudũya ado, mimĩ odug wõ yen. Tamo tenebur difar mog, mimĩ odug age fiya taka to wõ yen, mimĩ are gai odug bagai.  
\v 19 Taun odug Babilon are faraf towo fen, agef fen, teneub ganan nẽ taun daũ feledin. Negur ĩ Babilon Odug nigin weder fokõf fen, kap yogon didi barikã nẽ wain isokosen anĩ ifenen.  
\v 20 Nuyo ganan sa kele di, areig ilediya kisi feleya sã.  
\v 21 Saa ilunem uyẽ ais ado odug, teke tekelei 50 kilogram age fiya tamo bun kuku ren. Age fe di, idi uyẽ ais adom daũ fedin nigin de fen, Negur kono difen, ere nigin, daũ fiya are, gai sane bagai.   
\c 17  
\s1 Kayau Gaar Kuĩ Teten Ibodon  
\p
\v 1 Engel sewen beĩ sewen adodo anĩ takam isi fen, aya irokanan, “Usi, aya kayau bouwa na sur fedig odug, ĩ naan musei teten ibodõdig anĩ nẽ kafĩ fiya afelnõf.  
\v 2 Tenebur nẽ king, ĩ geid seseirã tobonunã dino di, tamo kayau tenebur difaref anidi, yogon seseirã tobonunã nẽ wain bunem, idi meleid waĩ yen.”   
\p
\v 3 Age ye fen, engel ĩ Awa Uur bunem aya gerere tuan yale irouleyan. An aya, kayau, gaar kuĩ giriya, bouwa bun kono fiya yeneid barikã, mudur sewen ado, karat ten anĩ teten ibod mog, ailen.  
\v 4 Kayau ĩ, kolos giriya tu releya medeĩya ado giriya bagai ifoun ken, gol, meein meli bagai ado, maaĩ tuwa meli bagai pel naki yen. Ĩ gol kap, ninir safineid ado yogon seseirã tobonunã nẽ sisik isokosen anĩ imam iroun.  
\v 5 Waa nẽ yana are, yogon dama bun ditoton:  
\pc BABILON ODUG  
\pc KAYAU BOUWEID NA SUR FIYA ADO  
\pc TENEBUR NINIR IBODOK ANIDI NEID SINA.   
\m
\v 6 Aya, kayau, Negur nẽ tamo kayau neid naudeid ado, idi Jesus nẽ od kurõ difesin anidi, nedi naudeid yokon, mala waĩ ye mog, ailen.  
\p Aya kayau anĩ ail fen, fatuk bagai terẽ aun.  
\v 7 Age afe di, engel aya irokanan, “Õ ere nigin terẽ wof? Aya, õ, kayau nẽ waa ado, gaar kuĩ kayau anĩ teten ibodõdig, ĩ mudur sewen ado fen, karat ten ado anĩ nẽ waa anĩ faded ayõf.  
\v 8 Gaar kuĩ ulen are, kulu ibodon, gama ibodõya sã, agef fen, ĩ ku isil idĩya sã bunem ulõ yeis fen, yogo daũ falauf bun ilauf. Tamo kayau tenebur dibodok anidi, saa teneub ado kare fen sain bunem isin, idi yeneid mata ibodõya nẽ buk bun to itoton, idi gaar kuĩ anĩ dile fen terẽ douf, ere nigin, gaar kuĩ ĩ kulu ibodon, gama ibodõya sã, agef fen, fau dum isiyouf.   
\p
\v 9 “Enei keleĩya nigin, kisi biya adouf. Mudur sewen are, arei mudu sewen kayau teten ibodõdig anĩ.  
\v 10 Idig king sewen anidi. Faif idi kuku ralaisin, taka fau ibodok, taka fau isiya sã. Anĩ ere, ĩ isiyouf are, sain naal bagai ibodõf.  
\v 11 Gaar kuĩ kulu ibodon, gama ibodõya sã, are ĩ namba eit king, ĩ sewen anidi nẽ taka, ĩ yogo daũ fiya bun ilauf.   
\p
\v 12 “Karat ten õ ulen are, ten king idi tano fau yaleya sã anidi, anĩ ere, idi gaar kuĩ geid, aua tekelei king nẽ megeir dalouf.  
\v 13 Idi kisi tekelei ado fen, dogo neid megeir ado totol, gaar kuĩ difenẽf.  
\v 14 Idi Sipsip Naal geid kusĩ douf, anĩ ere, Sipsip Naal idi kusĩ bun wal fediyouf, ere nigin, ĩ odug neid Odug ado king neid King. Idi ĩ iweignẽdin anĩ, igirnẽdin anĩ, feseya sã dõ difen anidi, ĩ geid difarauf.”   
\p
\v 15 Age ye fen, engel aya irokanan, “Naan, kayau bouwa na sur fedig ĩ anĩ teten ibodon, õ ulen are, tamo kayau, guru fiya odug, teneub ganan ado, od fire fire ganan.  
\v 16 Karat ten õ ulen ado gaar kuĩ, idi kayau bouwa na sur fedig anĩ to orodiyouf. Idi ĩ daũ difiye ken, gemũ dinenẽf. Idi ĩ bouwa dokon, yã nem tõ difiyẽf.  
\v 17 Negur idi neid waud bun kisi anĩ ino di, idi Negur nẽ oroya dõ difouf nigin, idi kisi tekelei dino fen, dogo neid tano gaar kuĩ difenẽf, age difef dile mog, Negur nẽ od kisi falauf.  
\v 18 Kayau õ ulen are, taun odug, tenebur nẽ king neid mudur ibodok anĩ.”   
\c 18  
\s1 Babilon Narĩ Fen  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya engel taka saa ilunem isi mog, ailen. Ĩ megeir odug ado, age fe di, yogon fula fiya medeĩya anim teneub lalan len.  
\v 2 Ĩ ait odugem, totol bagai iweig iron:  
\q1 “Kubũ yen! Babilon Odug kubũ yen!  
\q2 Ĩ, kaa sesen neid fõ,  
\q1 kaa sesen ganan neid fõ ado,  
\q2 ninã amuyẽ ado ninir sane to ile oroya ganan neid fõ falei fen.   
\q1
\v 3 Teneub ganan,  
\q2 yogon seseirã tobonunã nẽ wain totol don.  
\q1 Tenebur nẽ king, ĩ geid seseirã tobonunã dinon,  
\q2 age fe di, tenebur nẽ bisnis tamo idi, yogon safina nigin oroya totol ado bunem, safina musei dalen.”   
\p
\v 4 Anĩ bure fele di, aya ait taka saa ilunem eig ye mog, karĩ aun:  
\q1 “Neu tamo kayau, ã yogon mosor anĩ utin to walogouf nigin ado,  
\q2 ã in mala solo sane taka to walogouf nigin,  
\q2 ã ĩ utornẽg fen, usig,   
\q1
\v 5 ere nigin, yogon mosor mogo mudu ilun isel saa ilune di,  
\q2 Negur yogon idododin nigin weder fokõ yen.   
\q1
\v 6 Ĩ ifenein kilei abag wenẽgouf,  
\q2 ereb ĩ age fen are, ĩ age fen anĩ ado, taka teten unog fen, wenẽgouf.  
\q2 Ereb ĩ yogon kap bun falei fen are, ĩ falei fen anĩ ado, taka falei ge fen, teten unogouf.   
\q1
\v 7 Ĩ fula fiya medeĩya ado safina meli meli, yogo nigin yalen kilei,  
\q2 darau ado wau gudũ fiya fatuk bagai wenẽgouf.  
\q1 Ĩ yogon wau bun, yogo yana yales fen,  
\q2 ‘Aya kuin abodok, aya waab sã,  
\q2 agef fen, aya to bagai wau gudũ fouf,’ yen.   
\q1
\v 8 Anĩ nigin, naa taka bun, in daũ fiyẽya nẽ sesen ĩ bun isiyouf,  
\q2 are laa, wau gudũ fiya ado, kadir.  
\q1 Agef fen, ĩ yã bun isaikalauf,  
\q2 ere nigin, Odug Negur ĩ es fiyek, ĩ anĩ megeir barikã.   
\p
\v 9 “Tenebur nẽ king idi, ĩ geid seseirã tobonunã dino fen, yogon safina meli meli foi difen anidi, ĩ isaĩ di, kaau dile fen, idi ĩ nigin waud gudũf fen, inã logurouf.  
\v 10 Idi in darau yaleya anĩ nigin fatuk bagai kumĩ de fen, gerõ difar fen, dirõf:  
\q1 “‘Malalon! Malalon, O taun odug,  
\q2 O Babilon, taun megeir ado!  
\q1 Aua tekelei bun, ogon daũ fiya mogo isin!’   
\p
\v 11 “Tenebur nẽ bisnis tamo idi ĩ nigin waud gudũf fen, inã logurouf, ere nigin, taka nem idi neid safina baban to na yalouf,  
\v 12 safina are, gol, silwa, meein meli meli ado, maaĩ tuwa meli bagai pel; gabar lalau medeĩya, gabar giriya tu releya medeĩya, gabar slika ado, gabar giriya bagai; aa meli meli fire fire; ereb ereb fire fire elefan karat nem, aa meli meli nem, bras nem, ain nem ado, mambol nem dinodin;  
\v 13 sinamon, ye, aa gaula sumeĩ nigin tõ fiyadig, moul aa bun tamal sumeĩ biya biya ado, moul biya takag; wain ado oliv moul; flawa ado wit, bulmakau ado sipsip; hos ado karis, ferfer ado tamo mata dibodok.   
\p
\v 14 “Idi dirõf, ‘Ereb ereb yaleya nigin õ oroyon are, mogo sa kelen. Ogon safina musei ado ereb ereb fula fiya medeĩya ganan, mogo sa kelen, idi baban to bagai fotou difouf.’  
\v 15 Bisnis tamo safina eneidi na sur dife fen, ĩ bunem safina musei dalen anidi, yogon darau nigin fatuk bagai kumĩ de fen, gerõ difarauf. Idi inã logur fen, waud gudũf fen,  
\v 16 diweig dirõf:  
\q1 “‘Malalon! Malalon, O taun odug,  
\q2 kolos lalau meli bagai, giriya tu releya medeĩya ado, giriya bagai ifoun ken,  
\q2 gol, meein meli bagai ado, maaĩ tuwa meli bagai pel naki yen!   
\q1
\v 17 Aua tekelei bun dogol, safina odug bagai age fiya daũ felen!’  
\p “Maaĩ bun ulum irouya tamo ganan, idi waag bun diyõdig ganan ado, idi maaĩ bunem dogo neid mata ibodõya nẽ safina daledig anidi ganan, gerõ bagai difarauf.  
\v 18 Sain idi ĩ isaĩ di, kaau dile fen, idi diweig dirõf, ‘Taun odug eig fiya taka tau ibodon?’  
\v 19 Idi aas mudureid bun digu ken, waud gudũ fe di, inã logur fen, diweig dirõf:  
\q1 “‘Malalon! Malalon, O taun odug,  
\q2 an idi maaĩ bun waag adon ganan,  
\q2 yogon safina odug bunem safina musei dalen!  
\q1 Aua tekelei bun, are daũ felen!   
\q1
\v 20 O saa ilun, ĩ nigin waũ kulĩ ye!  
\q2 Negur nẽ tamo kayau, aposel ado, profet, wauĩ kulĩg!  
\q1 Ĩ ã age yein kilei, Negur ĩ es fiyen.’”   
\p
\v 21 Age ye fen, engel megeir ado, meein odug wit itutuya nẽ age fiya, yale fen, maaĩwõ ira ken, iron:  
\q1 “Waila sane eig fiya bunem,  
\q2 Babilon taun odug agef daũ fe di,  
\q2 baban to bagai dilouf.   
\q1
\v 22 Harp kodẽya tamo, seg tamo, kelel fĩya tamo ado, taur fũya tamo,  
\q2 idi neid ailõ õ bun baban to bagai karĩ douf.  
\q1 Kabĩ fire fire ganan nẽ keleĩ tamo,  
\q2 õ bun baban taka to bagai wõ youf.  
\q1 Wit itutuya nẽ meein ait,  
\q2 õ bun baban to bagai karĩ douf.   
\q1
\v 23 Lam nẽ lalan õ bun baban to bagai so fouf.  
\q1 Tamo kayau yalef yalef yeya ait,  
\q2 õ bun baban to bagai wõ youf.  
\q1 Ogon bisnis tamo idi, teneub ganan nẽ tamo odug.  
\q2 Õ ogon idegẽya kosẽ bunem, teneub ganan udegnẽdin.   
\q1
\v 24 Profet, Negur nẽ tamo kayau ado,  
\q2 tenebur ein didenkesin anidi ganan neid naudeid, ĩ bun dilen.”   
\c 19  
\s1 Halleluya!  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya saa ilun tamo kayau guru fiya mala odug neid aiteid gou reya gen, karĩ aun:  
\q1 “Halleluya!  
\q1 Kel gei fiya, fula fiya medeĩya ado, megeir are, neda Negur nẽ.   
\q1
\v 2 Yogon es fiya are, momoi fen madur bagai.  
\q1 Ĩ kayau bouwa na sur fedig odug,  
\q2 ĩ yogon seseirã tobonunã bunem teneub daũ fen anĩ, es fiyen.  
\q1 Ĩ yogon ferfer neid naudeid, anĩ mala solo ĩ bun ifenen.”   
\m
\v 3 Idi baban diweig diron:  
\q1 “Halleluya!  
\q1 Ĩ bunem kaau faimud gai gai iselauf.”   
\p
\v 4 Mudur adodo tuwenti-fo ado, ereb mata ibodõya aiwa adodo, kuku de fen, Negur king nẽ sia bun ibodon anĩ yana dalesen. Age de fen, idi diweig diron:  
\q1 “Momoi, Halleluya!”   
\p
\v 5 Age dife di, ait taka, king nẽ sia bunem wõ ye fen, iron:  
\q1 “Ã in ferfer ganan,  
\q2 ĩ anini wiyẽgedig,  
\q1 nanaal ado odudug,  
\q2 neda Negur yana waleseg!”   
\p
\v 6 Age ye di, aya guru fiya mala odug aiteid gen karĩ aun, are naan fatuk wĩ ye fen, gou redig gen ado, kolimei gudũya odug gen, diweig dirõ mog, karĩ aun:  
\q1 “Halleluya!  
\q2 Ere nigin, neda Odug Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri feid uyu iroudig anĩ, ĩ lo fiya nigin king ibodok.   
\q1
\v 7 Ada wauda kulĩ ye, wauda al fe fen,  
\q2 fula fiya medeĩya tafenẽf!  
\q1 Ere nigin, Sipsip Naal kayau yaleya nẽ naa mogo isin,  
\q2 age fe di, yogon kayau mois mogo yogo nigin dodok fen.   
\q1
\v 8 Kolos lalau meli bagai, medeĩya ado filiya,  
\q2 ĩ ifonũf nigin ifenen.”  
\m (Kolos lalau meli bagai are, Negur nẽ tamo kayau neid tobonuneid madur anĩ.)   
\p
\v 9 Anĩ bure fele di, engel aya irokanan, “Utot: ‘Idi Sipsip Naal kayau mois ado bagu fiya nẽ sifa bun ibodõya nigin iweignẽdin are, idi el fedif!’” Age ye fen, ĩ tobol fe iron, “Enei are, Negur nẽ od momoi bagai.”   
\p
\v 10 Age fe di, aya ĩ yana alesauf nigin, ye gariyan kubũ aun. Anĩ ere, ĩ aya irokanan, “To ago! Aya, õ ado, ogon turã tar idi Jesus nẽ wogõya kafĩ difel dirouf anidi geid, ada in ferfer. Negur yana wales! Ere nigin, Jesus nigin wogõya are, profet od wogõya nẽ uur anĩ.”   
\s1 Tamo Hos Lalau Teten Ibodon  
\p
\v 11 Aya saa ilun kã feleya ifar mog, aya wageun an hos lalau ifar mog, ailen. Tamo anĩ teten ibodon are, yana ‘Feseya Sã Dõ Fiya Biya’ ado ‘Momoi Bagai’ dedig. Madur bagai bunem, ĩ es feid fen, kusĩ yedig.  
\v 12 Yogon mala are, yã mala fitotoleya gen, agef fen, yogon mudur bun teter musei biya. Ĩ yogo bun yana itotoya taka ado, are aibem taka to keleĩ, ĩ yogo dogol.  
\v 13 Ĩ kolos meluk naud bun nu fen anĩ ifonun. Yogon yana are, Negur nẽ Od.  
\v 14 Saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo, idi hos lalau tetedin dibodada ken, kolos meli bagai, lalau filiya difoun ken, ĩ dõ difiyen.  
\v 15 Ĩ yogon awa bunem, dimig waila ado, teneub ganan yũf nigin wõ yen. “Ĩ ain manig nem ulum iroukenẽdiyouf.”\f + \fr 19:15  \ft Sam 2:9\f* Ĩ, Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri feid uyu iroudig anĩ nẽ didi totol nẽ wain asi fiya modoũ bun, asi fouf.  
\v 16 Ĩ, yogon kolos meluk bun ado yogon tukuri bun, yana enei itotoya ibodok:  
\pc KING NEID KING ADO ODUG NEID ODUG.   
\p
\v 17 Age afe fen, aya engel taka gaa bun ifar mog, ailen, ĩ ait odugem ninã ganan ilun fatutu def anidi iweig irokenẽdin, “Usig, Negur nẽ sifa odug bun gurug,  
\v 18 agog fen, ã, king bouweid, kusĩ mudur bouweid, tamo megeir adodo neid bouweid, hos ado hos tetedin dibodadak anidi neid bouweid, tamo kayau ganan, kafĩ fiya sã tamo ado ferfer, nanaal ado odudug, bouweid wãgauf.”   
\p
\v 19 Anĩ bure fele di, aya, gaar kuĩ, tenebur nẽ king ado, dogo neid kusĩ tamo idi, tamo hos teten ibodon anĩ, yogon kusĩ tamo geid weim kusĩ douf nigin, guru de mog, ailedin.  
\v 20 Anĩ ere, gaar kuĩ are dale diroun, age de fen, idegẽya profet, ĩ memelik nẽ uris gaar kuĩ mala bun inodin anĩg, gaar kuĩ ado dale diroun. Uris anidi bunem, ĩ, idi gaar kuĩ nẽ uris dalen anidi ado, idi yogon malakanon yana dalesedig anidi idegnẽdin. Idi urom mata dibod mog, ku kolili fiya meein salfa yã bobo reya barikã ado bun, gei de diraran.  
\v 21 Dogo neid kusĩ tamo ganan, dimig, tamo hos teten ibodon awa bunem wõ yen anim, idenkesin, age fe di, ninã ganan idi neid bouweid dõ dõ, teid isokosen.   
\c 20  
\s1 Tausen Yar  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya engel taka saa ilunem, ĩ ku isil idĩya sã nẽ ki ado, sen odug imam irou fen, isi mog, ailen.  
\v 2 Ĩ gogour odug, gogour kulu tamal bagai, are Devil be Satan dedig anĩ yale fen, tausen yar ifarauf nigin sen nem ifokelen.  
\v 3 Ĩ ku isil idĩya sã bun ira ken, ku katĩ fel fen, anĩ teten ĩtãfiya uris inon. Ĩ tenebur tamo kayau to idegneĩd mog, tausen yar ilauf nigin age fen. Anĩ bure fele di, sain tobega dogol ĩ folõ fiyekalauf.   
\p
\v 4 Aya, king nẽ sia anidi bun, idi es fiya nẽ megeir ifenẽdin anidi dibod mog, ailedin. Age afe fen, aya, dogo neid biya od Jesus nigin wogõ den ado, Negur nẽ od nigin, uleid kokour difedin anidi neid meleidkanon ailen. Idi gaar kuĩ be, yogon malakanon yana to dales fen, yogon uris demeid bun be, imeid bun to dalen. Idi mata ke de, fã de fen, Kristus geid, lo fiya nigin tausen yar ilauf anĩ nẽ mudur dibodon.  
\v 5 (Tamo gare den tunĩ ganan to ke de, fã de mog, tausen yar are bure felen.) Enei are, kel fãya uyulil anĩ.  
\v 6 Idi kel fãya uyulil anĩ bun ke de, fã den are, idi el feid fen, fateul. Laa uyulil anĩ dõ fiya isif are, idi bun megeir sã. Anĩ ere, idi Negur nẽ ado Kristus nẽ pris dibod ken, tausen yar anĩ bun, Kristus geid, lo fiya nigin mudur dibodõf.   
\s1 Satan Daũ Felen  
\p
\v 7 Tausen yar anĩ bure fele di, Satan ĩ yogon kalabus bun tamal yalelnẽ di,  
\v 8 ĩ tamo kayau teneub ganan bun idegnẽdiyouf nigin, teneub idĩyan aiwa adodo, are Gog ado Magog bun ile fen, idi kusĩ bun ileya nigin gou fediyouf. Idi neid namba are, maaĩ ubun mumul ifaref age fiya.  
\v 9 Idi teneub modoũ odug bun dile fen, Negur nẽ tamo kayau neid modoũ ado, taun Negur anĩ nigin wau laa fedig anĩ salili difen. Anĩ ere, yã saa ilunem isi fen, idi yakur feidlen.  
\v 10 Age fe di, Satan idi idegnẽdin are, ku kolili fiya meein salfa yã bobo reya ado bun dale diran, gaar kuĩ ado idegẽya profet idi ketem mogo an diraran. Idi ganan an sain ganan, bõ ado gaa ado, gai gai darau dalouf.   
\s1 Gare Den Anidi Es Fediyouf  
\p
\v 11 Anĩ bure fele di, aya king nẽ sia lalau odug ado, taka anĩ teten ibodon anĩ ailen. Teneub ado saa, ĩ mala iran nẽ waĩf yale di, idi modoũ san.  
\v 12 Age fe di, aya, gare den anidi, odudug ado nanaal, sia wagen difaren ado, buk ikoudiya anidig ailedin. Buk takag ikouya ailen are, mata ibodõya nẽ buk. Gare den anidi, ereb age difen buk bun itoton anĩ kilei, es fedin.  
\v 13 Maaĩ bun gare den anidi, maaim ifenẽdi di, laa ado Hades, gare de di, idi bun difaren anidi difenẽdin. Age fe di, mugu mugu ereb age difen kilei, es fedin.  
\v 14 Age fe di, laa ado Hades, ku kolili fiya yã bobo reya ado bun geif iraran. Ku kolili fiya yã bobo reya ado, are laa uyulil isin anĩ dõ fiya laa anĩ.  
\v 15 Aib taka ĩ, yogon yana mata ibodõya nẽ buk bun itotoya sã ilen, ĩ ku kolili fiya yã bobo reya ado bun, yale iran.   
\c 21  
\s1 Jerusalem Mata  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, aya, saa mata ado teneub mata, ailen. Saa uyulil ado teneub uyulil are waĩf yalen, agef fen, maaĩ baban to ibodon.  
\v 2 Aya Taun Fateul, are Jerusalem mata, Negur bun tamal, saa ilunem isi mog, ailen, are kayau mois tamon ileya nigin naki rel fen, dodok fen gen.  
\v 3 Age afe fen, aya ait odug king nẽ sia bunem eig ye mog, karĩ aun, “Gama Negur nẽ salafat, tamo bun ibodok, age fe di, ĩ idi geid dibodõf. Idi yogon tamo kayau ouf, age fe di, Negur yogo bagai, idi geid dibod ken, idi neid Negur ibodõf.  
\v 4 Ĩ idi neid meleid bun maruid ganan waĩ falauf. Baban laa, wau gudũ fiya, inã yaleya be, darau to ibodõf, ere nigin, ereb ereb tubu nẽ are, ganan sa kelen.”   
\p
\v 5 Ĩ king nẽ sia bun ibodon are iron, “Aya ereb ereb ganan mata anof!” Age ye fen, ĩ iron, “Enei utot, ere nigin, od eneidi are, agef bagai wõ youf nigin momoi bagai.”   
\p
\v 6 Ĩ aya irokanan, “Gama mogo bure felen. Aya uyulil ado idikeleya, gariya ado idikeleya. Taka ĩ naan ail fouf, aya ĩ mata ifenẽya nẽ naan warur bun tamal, mala sã, afenẽ di, yãf.  
\v 7 Taka ĩ kusĩ wal fouf, ĩ enei ganan akorouf, age fe di, aya yogon Negure di, ĩ neu kesu ibodõf.  
\v 8 Anĩ ere, idi dume dume age difedig, momoiya sã, tobonunã sane bagai dinodig, tamo dukesidig, noli tobonunã dinodig, idegẽya bun kosẽ dedig, idegẽya waitou yana dalesedig ado, idegẽya tamo ganan, idi neid modoũ are, ku kolili fiya meein salfa yã bobo reya barikã ado bun. Enei are, laa uyulil dõ fiya namba tu laa anĩ.”   
\p
\v 9 Engel sewen anĩ taka, beĩ sewen idikeleya nẽ sesen barikã teneub daũ fiya nẽ ado anĩ taka, isi fen, aya irokanan, “Usi, aya kayau mois, Sipsip Naal nẽ kayau anĩ afelnõf.”  
\v 10 Age ye fen, ĩ aya Awa Uur bunem arei odug ilun bagai anĩ bun irouleya fen, Taun Fateul, Jerusalem, Negur bun tamal saa ilunem isi mog, ifelnan.  
\v 11 Taun are, Negur nẽ fula fiya medeĩya anim so fen. Yogon medeĩya are, meein na sur fiya nẽ meli bagai jaspa gen, yogon filiya are, galas medeĩya bagai gen.  
\v 12 Taun are, yogon garaĩ odug ilun fen, bobog tuwelf ado. Agef fen, engel tuwelf bobog bun difaren. Bobog bun, Israel ibor tuwelf anidi yeneid itoton.  
\v 13 Bobog towo gaa iseyan, bobog towo not melẽ, bobog towo saut melẽ, bobog towo gaa ileyan age de difaren.  
\v 14 Taun anĩ nẽ garaĩ, gariya tuwelf ado, gariya tuwelf anĩ bun, Sipsip Naal nẽ aposel tuwelf yeneid ado.   
\p
\v 15 Engel aya wogõ fiyan are, ĩ taun, taun nẽ bobog ado, yogon garaĩ sisi fediyouf nigin, sisi fiya nẽ gol tibog iroun.  
\v 16 Taun nẽ bagalam ado bogorou kilei kilei inon. Engel are tibog nem taun sisi fe fen, ilen, 2,200 kilomita meluk, yogon bagalam ado yogon ilun areg de anĩ kilei.  
\v 17 Engel ĩ, tamo nẽ sisi fiya bunem, taun garaĩ nẽ mugi sisi fen, are 65 mita, areg engel nẽ sisi fiya.  
\v 18 Garaĩ are, meein jaspa nem inon. Agef fen, taun are gol bagai nem dogol inon, gol filiya are galas medeĩya bagai gen.  
\v 19 Taun garaĩ nẽ gariya are, meein meli bagai fire fire nem, naki fen. Gariya uyulil ifaren are jaspa nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein maaĩ gegẽ gen sapaia nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein kalsedoni nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein aarau mata gen emeral nem,  
\v 20 anĩ dõ fiya are meein giriya ado lalau sadonikis nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein giriya konilian nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein aarau mayo gen krisolait nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein aarau mata gen beril nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein aarau mayo gen topas nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein krispres nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein haiasin nem, anĩ dõ fiya are meein giriya ametis nem.  
\v 21 Bobog tuwelf are maaĩ tuwa meli bagai pel tuwelf, bobog teke tekelei, maaĩ tuwa meli bagai pel teke tekelei nem inon. Taun nẽ naab odug are, galas karẽtut bagai gen, gol bagai nem dogol inon. \fig Kilelei maaĩ tuwa meli bagai pel nem dinon.|src="lb00171c.tif" size="span" ref="21:21" \fig*   
\p
\v 22 Aya taun an tempel taka to ailen, ere nigin, Odug Negur saa ilun nẽ kusĩ tamo guri feid uyu iroudig anĩ ado Sipsip Naal are, idi anĩ tempel.  
\v 23 Taun are, gaa lalan be, ogõ lalan yaleya nigin to yenek, ere nigin, Negur nẽ fula fiya medeĩya anim lalan ifenẽdig, agef fen, Sipsip Naal are taun nẽ lam.  
\v 24 Tenebur tamo kayau, taun anĩ nẽ lalan bun diyõ di, tenebur nẽ king, nedi fula fiya medeĩya, taun anĩ bun dirousiyouf.  
\v 25 Naa taka bun, yogon bobog taka to bagai inolalauf, ere nigin, an bõ sãf.  
\v 26 Tenebur tamo kayau idi, nedi fula fiya medeĩya ado yana odug, taun anĩ bun dirou disiyouf.  
\v 27 Ereb taka amuyẽ ado an namen to ilauf, agef fen, aib taka mama nẽ tobonunã age fedig be, idegẽdig, ĩg an to ilauf, anĩ ere, idi yeneid Sipsip Naal nẽ mata ibodõya nẽ buk bun itoton anidi dogol dilauf.   
\c 22  
\s1 Mata Ifenẽya Nẽ Naan Odug  
\p
\v 1 Anĩ bure fele di, engel ĩ, aya, naan odug, mata ifenẽya nẽ naan, are karẽtut galas medeĩya bagai gen, Negur nẽ ado Sipsip Naal nẽ king nẽ sia bunem isif anĩ ifelnan,  
\v 2 naan are taun nẽ naab odug atu isilen. Naan si sitakã, mata ifenẽya nẽ aa difaren, are yar tekelei bun faat yũ tuwelf fedig, ogõ teke tekelei bun yogon faat yũdig. Agef fen, aa aarau are, tenebur tamo kayau dagi yalelkenẽdiya nẽ.  
\v 3 Isisĩya taka baban to ibodõf. Negur nẽ ado Sipsip Naal nẽ king nẽ sia are, taun namen ibodõf, age fe di, yogon ferfer idi, in aruna dalouf.  
\v 4 Idi in nawa dilouf, age dife di, yogon yana idi demeid bun ibodõf.  
\v 5 Baban bõ taka to ibodõf. Idi lam nẽ lalan be, gaa nẽ lalan nigin, to kisi difouf, ere nigin, Odug Negur idi lalan ifenẽdiyouf. Age fe di, idi gai gai lo fiya nigin mudur dibodõf.  
\v 6 Engel ĩ aya irokanan, “Od eneidi are, agef bagai wõ youf nigin momoi bagai. Odug, profet neid uur nẽ Negur, ĩ ereb mogo wõ youf bagai anĩ yogon ferfer ifelnẽdiyouf nigin, yogon engel sur fen.”   
\s1 Jesus Mogo Isif  
\p
\v 7 “Ulef! Aya mogo kaisã bagai asiyou fenẽ! Taka ĩ profet od buk enei bun ibodok anĩ dõ fef are, ĩ el fiyek.”   
\p
\v 8 Aya, Jon, ayam eneidi karĩ au fen, ailedin. Sain aya anĩ karĩ au fen, ailedin, aya engel aya ifelnan anĩ, ye gariyan kubũ au fen, yana alesauf nigin age afen.  
\v 9 Anĩ ere, ĩ aya irokanan, “To ago! Aya, õ, ogon turã tar profet ado, idi buk enei nẽ od dõ difef anidi ganan geid, ada in ferfer. Negur yana wales!”   
\p
\v 10 Age ye fen, ĩ aya irokanan, “Õ buk enei nẽ profet od anĩ bun, ĩtãfiya uris to uno, ere nigin, sain mogo melsak.  
\v 11 Aib ĩ mosor inof, utornẽg len, ĩ agef mosorei youf. Aib ĩ sane age fef, utornẽg len, ĩ sane agei fouf. Aib ĩ biya age fef, utornẽg len, ĩ biya agei fouf. Aib ĩ fateul ibodok, utornẽg len, ĩ fateulei youf.”   
\p
\v 12 Jesus irok, “Ulef! Aya mogo kaisã bagai asiyou fenẽ! Mala solo tamo ifenẽdiya nẽ are yeir, aya bun ibodok, anĩ nigin, aya, tamo mugu mugu ereb age difen kilei anĩ afenẽdiyouf.  
\v 13 Aya uyulil ado idikeleya, uyulil nẽ ado dumen bagai nẽ, gariya ado idikeleya.   
\p
\v 14 “Idi dogo neid kolos meluk kulo difef, anĩ bunem, idi mata ifenẽya nẽ aa bun ileya nigin ado, taun nẽ bobog bunem taun namen ileya nigin kisi feleya, are idi el fedif.  
\v 15 Mayarẽ difaref are, idi gaũ, idi idegẽya bunem kosẽ dedig, noli tobonunã dinodig, tamo dukesidig, idegẽya waitou yana dalesedig ado, idi ganan idegẽya nigin waud laaf fen, age difedig anidi.   
\p
\v 16 “Aya, Jesus, ayam kurõ fesiya od enei sios nigin afeneĩf nigin, ã bun neu engel sur afen. Aya Dawid nẽ Warumutei ado Ibor, Bonimei nẽ Barisa medeĩya.”   
\p
\v 17 Awa Uur ado kayau mois dirok, “Usi!” Aib taka ĩ karĩ yef, irõf, “Usi!” Aib taka ĩ naan ail fef, utornẽg len, ĩ isiyouf. Aib taka ĩ orof, utornẽg len, ĩ mata ifenẽya nẽ naan ege luwa yalouf.   
\p
\v 18 Aya, idi ganan buk enei nẽ profet od karĩ def anĩ, totol bagai arokenẽdif: Aibem taka od enei teten ereb taka tobol fouf, Negur ĩ daũ fiya nẽ sesen buk enei bun itoton anĩ, ĩ bun tobol fouf.  
\v 19 Agef fen, aib taka profet od nẽ buk enei bun od taka yalelauf, Negur ĩ, mata ifenẽya nẽ aa ado taun fateul, buk enei bun faded fel itoton anidi bun tamal, ĩ yalelnẽf.   
\p
\v 20 Taka ĩ enei ganan kurõ fesif, are irok, “Momoi, aya mogo kaisã bagai asiyou fenẽ.”  
\p Momoi. Odug Jesus usi.   
\p
\v 21 Odug Jesus nẽ wau ifenẽya, Negur nẽ tamo kayau bun ibodõf. Momoi.   